 the postcode, so please enter the full address.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Drop off your car at Airparks on your way to the airport. The fully-insured staff will park your car for you.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Just catch the shuttle bus back to the car park from the same place where you were dropped off. You'll need to show the ticket you were given when you checked in to the driver. After you've collected your keys from reception, just drive to the exit barrier, and scan the barcode attached to your keys to get out.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Birmingham Airparks is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0121 789 9323</helpline><distanceToAirport>Birmingham Airparks is located about 4 miles from the Terminal building.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Airparks operate transfers to and from the airport every 25 minutes, 24 hours a day which take 15 minutes. Please allow 30 minutes for checking in and transfer to the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>15 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The site is fully-fenced, has security cameras, 24 hour patrols, and a 'Park Mark' safer parking award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>All buses have disabled access.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/BHXL.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>BHXM</code><airport>BHX</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>CAR PARK 1</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Located next to the terminals.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;2 minute walk from the terminals.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Situated directly opposite the airport terminal&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Ideal for stays for just few hours or even longer&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>NCP Ltd, Birmingham International Airport, Airport Way, Birmingham, B26 3QJ</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From Birmingham City Centre: Take the A45 east towards Coventry.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the signs for Birmingham International Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; On entry to the airport follow the signs for Car Park 1.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M42: Exit the M42 at Junction 6.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the signs for Birmingham International Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; On entry to the airport follow the signs for Car Park&amp;nbsp; 1.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;h4&gt; Upon arrival&lt;/h4&gt;  &lt;p&gt; We have&amp;nbsp;number plate recognition in operation at this car park, you no longer need to push for a ticket. Our cameras will read your number plate and issue a ticket automatically. However, if you haven’t provided us with your registration number at the point of booking we won’t be able to automatically recognise you on arrival.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If you experience difficulty and have pre-booked with us please don’t push the button for a ticket, just push the help button and a member of our customer services team will assist you.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Drive to the&amp;nbsp;exit barrier and&amp;nbsp;insert your ticket for your pre booked parking to be validated. Once validated, the barrier will raise. If the barrier doesn't raise, please press the assistance button and have your booking reference available to quote to our customer services team.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If you have overstayed your booking, you will be able to pay for the overstay at the exit barrier by credit or debit card.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Car Park&amp;nbsp; 2 &amp;amp; 3 are open 365 days a year.&