><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0345 050 7080&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; Birmingham Car Park 5 is located on airport and is just a 5 minute bus ride from the from the terminals.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Courtesy transfers to and from the terminals take 5 minutes and operate every 10 minutes.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>5 minutes.</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Birmingham Car Park 5&amp;nbsp; is an official on-airport car park. It has CCTV, high security fencing, regular security patrols and has been granted the ‘Park Mark’ award for safer parking.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>1416</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>There are a number of Blue Badge bays available which are allocated on a first come-first serve basis. Courtesy buses have disabled access.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/BHXR.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>BHXY</code><airport>BHX</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>DRIVEFLY MEET &amp; GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;You will be called 20-30 minutes prior to your arrival time to confirm your drop off time.If you you do not receive a call, please call us when you are 15-20 minutes away from the terminal.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Meet &amp;amp; Greet.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Operates 24 hours.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;No transfer required.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Birmingham Drivefly Meet &amp;amp; Greet&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M42: Leave the M42 at Junction 6 and follow the signs for Birmingham International Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; On arriving at the airport, use the 'Drop &amp;amp; Go'&amp;nbsp;area immediately outside the terminal. As you take a parking ticket,proceed through the barrier and park your vehicle in the middle of the car park (next to the tall standing lamp posts). &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Here you will be greeted by one of our chauffeurs at the prearranged meeting point, who will have all your booking details and will be wearing a black jacket with our Drivefly company logo on it.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On arriving at the airport, use the 'Drop &amp;amp; Go' area immediately outside the terminal. Take the ticket from the barrier and immediately turn RIGHT. On the right hand side perimeter of the Drop and Go area you will see a number of parking bays. Please park in between bays 9-12.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Here you will be greeted by one of our chauffeurs at the prearranged meeting point, who will have all your booking details and will be wearing a black jacket with our Drivefly company logo on it.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Please call us on 0121 647 3683 / 07935 209 700 once you have collected all your luggage’s. In case of any delays please let us know.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Our chauffer will deliver your vehicle to the agreed pick up point at the airport.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; *Depending on the product you have paid for; you may be required to pay for the airport exit fee on your return. Please ask our driver for clarification.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>The car park is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0121 647 3683/07935 209 700&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Your car will be stored at secure car park close to airport. It is manned with 24-hour security, regular patrols and a high perimeter fence.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/BHXY.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>BHXZ</code><airport>BHX</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>MAPLE MANOR MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Licensed Meet &amp;amp; Greet Partners at Birmingham Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Over 21 years Meet and Greet experience&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Hassle-free chauffeur service - your vehicle is collected and returned to you at the airport.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;With over 21 years of Meet &amp;amp; Greet experience.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Hassle-free chauffeur service&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Collected and returned to your terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Maple Manor Parking, Drop &amp;amp; Go Car Park, Birmingham Airport&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Head Office Address - Maple Manor Parking, London Road, Crawley RH10 9SW&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Make sure you call the car park 15-20 minutes before you arrive on 01212 273 338. Enter option 1.&amp;nbsp; Take a ticket from the barrier with the sign saying 'maximum stay 10 minutes'. Turn immediately right and park in the number&amp;nbsp; bays 17-24 on your right.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Make sure you call the car park 15-20 minutes before you arrive on 0121 227 3338. Enter option 1. Take a ticket from the barrier, turn immediately right and park in the number bays 17-24 on your right. Your chauffeur will be waiting for you there and will be wearing a Maple Manor high-visibility jacket and carrying ID. They'll take your keys and park your car for you in a secured car park while you board your flight. Please give the entry ticket to your chauffeur.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If at anytime the above bays are full, You are allowed to park in unmarked bays on the far right or far left between bay no. 2 and 8 (this is only allowed if there is no available parking space in bays 17-20).&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Please call Maple Manor on 0121 2273 338 as soon as you have your luggage (or when you are ready for your car) and your car will be sent back on its way to you.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Return to the Drop and Go car park where you handed over your keys and this is where your chauffeur will meet you. He'll return your keys to you and hand you a ticket so you can get out of the car park without paying.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; Please do not call before you are ready for your car. If you call Maple Manor before you are ready for your car and subsequently the 10 minutes expires on your ticket, &amp;nbsp;then you may have to pay to exit the Drop &amp;amp; Go car park.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>The car park is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0121 227 3338&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; Just drop your car off outside the terminal and walk the rest of the way.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; The car park where your car will be stored is protected by CCTV, has a high fence, entry and exit barriers, floodlighting and regular patrols. It is also manned 24 hours a day.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&lt;p&gt; Parking is for cars only and your car must fit into a standard sized parking space. If your car does not fit into a stndard sized parking space or you are unsure, please call Maple Manor on 0121 2273 338 to discuss (extra charges may apply). Large vans, vehicles with more than 8 passenger seats, lorries, caravans, trailers and motorcycles are not accepted unless by special prior arrangement.&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; This parking service is perfect for disabled customers as there's no need to get a transfer bus.&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/BHXZ.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>BHX1</code><airport>BHX</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>MAPLE MANOR MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Licensed Meet and Greet Partners at Birmingham Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Over 21 years Meet and Greet experience.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Hassle-free chauffeur service - your vehicle is collected and returned to you at the airport.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Convenient Meet and Greet service&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;No transfers required&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Safe and Secure&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Hassle-free&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Maple Manor Parking, Drop &amp;amp; Go Car Park, Birmingham Airport&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Head Office Address - Maple Manor Parking, London Road, Crawley RH10 9SW&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;Make sure you call the car park 15-20 minutes before you arrive on 0121 227 3338. Enter option 1.&amp;nbsp;Take a ticket from the barrier with the sign sayng 'maximum stay 10 minutes'. Turn immediately right and park in the number bays 17-24 on your right.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; 