nd provide the operator with your pre-booking reference number and surname. The operator will then rise the barrier manually for you to exit.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; This car park is opened 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0845 319 2781&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>The Car Park is located within the airport boundary, a short walking distance away from the terminal building.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required as the car park is just a short walk from the terminal.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; This is an official on-airport car park, managed by Robin Hood Airport. They have high levels of security, with a high-tech CCTV system, electronically controlled entry and exit barriers, Automatic Number Plate Recognition, and 24 hour monitoring. All of the on-airport car parks at Robin Hood Airport hold the 'Park Mark' award for safer parking.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&lt;p&gt; There are no height restrictions at this car park, however please note that they do not allow trailers, or coaches. Any vehicles requiring more than one space must be booked via their call centre on 0845 319 2781.&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; Disabled parking spaces are located in all of our On-Airport Car Parks . Individual spaces cannot be reserved and are&amp;nbsp;always subject to availability.&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/DSAI.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>DSAA</code><airport>DSA</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>PLATINUM PARKING MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;The most convenient way to park when flying.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt; Your car is collected and returned to you at t