. This ticket both on entrance and exit allows 15 minutes “free parking” to complete both pick up and drop off for the client.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; On passing through the barriers please drive through the car park to the “Meet and Greet” zone which is the nearest possible parking point to the airport’s main terminal within the Short Stay Car Park.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; There you will be met there by a Platinum Parking representative.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; PLEASE CALL PLATINUM PARKING ON THEIR 24 HOUR MOBILE 07926 402830 THE DAY BEFORE YOUR ARRIVAL AT THE AIRPORT TO CONFIRM YOUR MEET AND GREET TIME IS STILL FINE.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; PLEASE CALL PLATINUM PARKING 15 MINUTES BEFORE YOUR ARRIVAL AS WE APPRECIATE ARRIVAL TIMES CAN CHANGE EN ROUTE.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; At the airport please follow signs for the “Short Stay Car Park” (located opposite the Ramada Hotel) and at the entrance barriers to the car park please take an admission ticket. This ticket both on entrance and exit allows 15 minutes “free parking” to complete both pick up and drop off for the client.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; On passing through the barriers please drive through the car park to the “Meet and Greet” zone which is the nearest possible parking point to the airport’s main terminal within the Short Stay Car Park.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; There you will be met there by a Platinum Parking representative.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; PROCEDURY LADOWANIA&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Zadzwo? Platinum Parking na ich 24 godzin telefonu 07926 402830 dzie? przed przyjazdem w celu potwierdzenia lotnisko spotykaj? abd pozdrawiam tw&amp;oacute;j czas jest parapet w porz?dku.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Zadzwo? Platinum Parking 15 minut przed przybyciem AS Doceniamy przylot&amp;oacute;w mo?na zmieni? w drodze.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Na lotnisku nale?y kierowa? si? znakami na &amp;quot;Short Stay Car Park&amp;quot; (znajduje si? naprzeciwko hotelu Ramada) oraz na bariery wej?cia na parking nale?y wzi?? bilet wst?pu. Ten bilet zar&amp;oacute;wno na wej?ciu i wyj?ciu pozwala na 15 minut &amp;quot;Bezp?atny parking&amp;quot;, aby zako?czy? oba odebra? i zasn?? dla klienta.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Na przej?ciu przez przejazd przez prosimy barier parkingu do &amp;quot;spotka? i pozdrowi?&amp;quot; strefy, kt&amp;oacute;ry jest najbli?szy mo?liwy punkt parkingowe do g?&amp;oacute;wnego terminala na lotnisku w Short Stay Car Park.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Tam spotka? si? z Tob? nie przez przedstawiciela Platinum parking.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Transfery nie s? wymagane z tej us?ugi, jak samoch&amp;oacute;d jest pobierana od Ciebie i wr&amp;oacute;ci? do ciebie na lotnisku.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; PROCEDURA WYJAZDU&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Po powrocie z powrotem do l?dowania w Doncaster Robin Hood Airport, gdy ju? wszystkie swoje baga?e z karuzeli baga?owej zadzwo? Platinum parking 24 godziny numer 07926 402830 mobilnych i Tw&amp;oacute;j samoch&amp;oacute;d zostanie zwr&amp;oacute;cone w miejscu, gdzie pierwotnie odstawili?my go w dniu przyjazdu.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On returning back to and landing at Doncaster Robin Hood&amp;nbsp; Airport, once you have ALL your baggage from the luggage carousel just call the Platinum Parking 24 hour mobile number 07926 402 830 and your car will be returned to you in the area where you originally dropped it off on your arrival.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>365 Day a year</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 07926 402830&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park has CCTV cameras and secured fencing. The whole car park is fully floodlit.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/DSAA.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>DSAB</code><airport>DSA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>PREMIUM</name><description>&lt;li&gt;The closest car park to the terminal building.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Dedicated entrance and exit route - no traffic hold ups.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Closest Car Park to terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Ultimate convenience.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Operates Automatic Number Plate Recognition system (ANPR).&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Doncaster Robin Hood Airport, DN9 3RH.</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the A1: Leave the A1(M) at Junction 34 (Blyth).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout take the A614 heading towards Bawtry.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The A614 runs into the A638 through Bawtry.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the A638 through Bawtry, heading north towards Doncaster.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Approximately 3&amp;frac12; miles after leaving Bawtry take a right turn into Hurst Lane, signposted for Auckley.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Proceed along Hurst Lane for approximately 1&amp;frac12; miles until you arrive at a set of traffic lights.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Turn right at these lights and continue forward along the dual carriageway towards Robin Hood Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for the 'Premium Car Park' on approach to the Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the West via the M62: Turn off the M62 at Junction 35 and follow the M18 southbound.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Leave the M18 at Junction 5 and head eastbound on the M180, leaving almost immediately at Junction 1.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take a right turn at the roundabout, heading south towards the A614 signposted for Bawtry.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for the A614 and Bawtry.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Travel through Hatfield Woodhouse and continue for approximately two miles into Blaxton.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the Blaxton roundabout turn right and follow the road, passing Walkers Nursery/Garden Centre on the left.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the next left into Gatehouse Lane.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;After crossing the railway line take the right turn at the roundabout and continue for approximately 200 yards.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The entrance to Robin Hood Airport is on the left.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for the 'Premium Car Park' on approach to the Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the East via the M180/M18: Follow the M180 to the end.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout, take the right hand lane and follow it all the way around, coming back on yourself so you are now heading eastbound on the M180 towards Scunthorpe.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Leave the motorway at Junction 1.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take a right turn at the roundabout, heading south towards the A614 signposted for Bawtry.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for the A614 and Bawtry.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Travel through Hatfield Woodhouse and continue for approximately two miles into Blaxton.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the Blaxton roundabout turn right and follow the road, passing Walkers Nursery/Garden Centre on the left.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the next left into Gatehouse Lane.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;After crossing the railway line take the right turn at the roundabout and continue for approximately 200 yards.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The entrance to Robin Hood Airport is on the left.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for the 'Premium Car Park' on approach to the Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>This car park operates an Automatic Number Plate Recognition system (ANPR). Please DO NOT insert a credit/debit card into the car park barrier as you will be charged again. Follow the signs for the Premium Car Park and Control Point 1. On the road towards the Premium car park you will pass through one set of barriers. Please proceed slowly whilst the barrier reads your number plate. The ANPR system will read the vehicle registration plate and the barrier will rise allowing you to enter. Continue forward and at the next roundabout, take the first exit, the Premium Car Park is on your right. On arrival at the Premium Car Park, the entry barrier will rise automatically - no ticket will be issued. If the ANPR system fails to recognize your registration, please press the help button located on the barriers for assistance.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>On your return to the airport, please collect your vehicle and drive to the exit barriers. The barrier will automatically lift allowing you to exit. Your booking will be validated by the Automatic Number Plate system on the exit lane barrier. If the system failed to recognise your vehicle when you arrived at the airport, please press the help button on the barrier and provide the operator with your pre-booking reference number and surname. The operator will then raise the barrier manually for you to exit.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; This car park is opened 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0845 319 2782&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>The Premium Flex Car Park is located adjacent to the terminal building - less than 60 seconds from terminal.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required as the car park is just a short walk from the terminal.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A