alidated by the Automatic Number Plate system on the exit lane barrier. If the system failed to recognise your vehicle when you arrived at the airport, please press the help button on the barrier and provide the operator with your pre-booking reference number and surname. The operator will then raise the barrier manually for you to exit.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; This car park is opened 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0845 319 2782&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; The Premium Pricebuster Car Park is located adjacent to the terminal building - less than 60 seconds from terminal.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required as the car park is just a short walk from the terminal.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; This is an official on-airport car park, managed by Robin Hood Airport. They have high levels of security, with a high-tech CCTV system, electronically controlled entry and exit barriers, Automatic Number Plate Recognition, and 24 hour monitoring. All of the on-airport car parks at Robin Hood Airport hold the 'Park Mark' award for safer parking.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&lt;p&gt; There are no height restrictions at this car park, however please note that they do not allow trailers, or coaches. Any vehicles requiring more than one space must be booked via their call centre on 0845 319 2781.&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>168</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; Disabled parking spaces are located in all of our On-Airport Car Parks . Individual spaces cannot be reserved and are&amp;nbsp;always subject to availability.&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/DSAH.jpg</logoURL></carPark></carParks></airport><airport code=\"DOV\"><name>Dover Port</name><shortname>doverport</shortname><terminals/><carParks><carPark><code>DOVC</code><airport>DOV</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>PORT PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Located only 1/2 a mile from Dover Port.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Free transfer - Only minutes away.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Full CCTV Coverage.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Free transfer.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Two minutes away for the Cruise Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Four minutes away for the Ferry Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Service available from 7am and 7pm.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Full CCTV Coverage.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Port Parking, Port House, South Military Road, Western Height&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Dover, Kent , CT17 9UE&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M20:&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the first roundabout as you enter Dover (Western Heights Roundabout) take the 1st exit.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; After 50 metres, turn right onto South Military Road. &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; After 200 metres the car park is on your left.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M2/A2:&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Exit the M2 at Junction 7 and take the A2 to Dover.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the Whitfield roundabout take the 2nd exit and follow the signs for Dover / Ferries. &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the next roundabout take the 2nd exit signed Dover / Ferries. Go down Jubilee Hill to the Eastern Docks Roundabout. Take the 1st exit signed A20 to Folkestone / Channel Tunnel. &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the A20 and go straight over until the fourth roundabout (Western Heights roundabout)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the Western Heights Roundabout take the 2nd exit and after 50 metres turn right onto South Military Road.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; After 200 metres the car park is on your left.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; When you arrive at the car park, drive up to the barrier, which will lift automatically. Find a space and park your car, then head over to reception to hand over your car keys.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;taking only 2 minutes to the Cruise Terminal or 4 minutes to the Ferry Terminal.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure></departureProcedure><openingPeriods></openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 01304 210880&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; Located only &amp;frac12; mile from Port of Dover Cruise Terminal and 1 &amp;frac12; miles from the Ferry Terminal.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Port Parking offers a free minibus transfer, on durations over one day - if duration is for one day a &amp;pound;5.00 transfer fee will apply, service operating between 7am and 7pm, taking only 2 minutes to the Cruise Terminal or 4 minutes to the Ferry Terminal.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>2 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; This car park has full CCTV coverage, electric security gates, security fencing and security lighting.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>8</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; This car park is suitable for disabled customers and has disabled spaces located near the reception area.&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/DOVC.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>DOVB</code><airport>DOV</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>RELYON CRUISE PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Situated only 3 miles from Dover Port's cruise terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Polite and friendly staff always at hand to load and unload your luggage.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Only 3 miles from Dover port's CRUISE terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Available for Cruise Only.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Polite and friendly staff.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Assisting with load and unload luggage.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Poulton Close, Coombe Valley Road, Dover, Kent, CT17 0HL</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M20/A20: Drive into Dover passing over 3 roundabouts before joining Snargate Street.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take the 1st exit off of the 4th roundabout leading to York Street.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the road to the next roundabout and take the 2nd exit onto Priory Road and then the High Street.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Continue through 4 sets of traffic lights and turn left into Coombe Valley Road at the 5th.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Continue to the next roundabout and take the 1st exit onto the Poulton Close Industrial Estate.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Continue for a short distance and the Relyon Cruise Parking is on the right just past Coombes Kitchen Cafe.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M2/A2: Exit the M2 at Junction 7 and take the A2 to Dover.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive directly into Dover and the Whitfield Roundabout where McDonalds is located.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take the 4th exit onto the A256/Whitfield Hill.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take the 1st exit off the next roundabout onto the A256/London Road.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Stay on this road, passing the 1st set of traffic lights at Crabble, and continue to the bottom of the road where you will find a 2nd set of lights adjacent to Hollis Motors.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Carry straight on at these lights, which will bring you into Buckland Avenue.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Carry straight on, then at the 3rd set of traffic lights turn right into Cherry Tree Avenue.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the next set of lights turn right and then take the 1st left into Coombe Valley Road.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Continue to the next roundabout and take the 1st exit onto the Poulton Close Industrial Estate.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Continue for a short distance and the Relyon Cruise Parking is on the right just past Coombes Kitchen Cafe.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Please allow at least 45 minutes for check in at the car park and transfer to the port. At peak periods additional time should be allowed.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Please arrive at the Car Park at least 45 minutes before you are due to check in at the Port. Customers are asked to drive direct to the compound and report to Reception. A member of Relyon staff will book your car in. You will then be asked to unload your luggage; we are more than willing to lend a hand if needed. When you have everything you need out of your car please hand in your car key to Reception. A Relyon bus driver will help you and your luggage into the Courtesy shuttle bus. We will also park your car for you.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure></departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>01304 201227 Fax:01304 240289</helpline><distanceToAirport>Conveniently located just 3&amp;frac12; miles from Dover Port.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Relyon Parking operate transfers to and from Dover Port on demand. Please allow 45 minutes for checking in and transfer to the port.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>10 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Vehicles are stored in a fully fenced secure compound with CCTV, that is manned 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/DOVB.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>DOVA</code><airport>DOV</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>RELYON FERRY PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Situated only 3 miles from Dover Ferry Port.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Polite and friendly staff always at hand to load and unload your luggage.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Situated 3 miles from Dover Ferry Port&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Polite and friendly staff&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Help in hand with loading and unloading luggage&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Poulton Close, Coombe Valley Road, Dover, Kent, CT17 0HL</address><directions>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M20/A20: Drive into Dover passing over 3 roundabouts before joining Snargate Street.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take the 1st exit off of the 4th roundabout leading to York Street.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the road to the next roundabout and take the 2nd exit onto Priory Road and then the High Street.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Continue through 4 sets of traffic lights and turn left into Coombe Valley Road at the 5th.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Continue to the next roundabout and take the 1st exit onto the Poulton Close Industrial Estate.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Continue for a short distance and the Relyon Ferry Parking is on the right just past Coombes Kitchen Cafe.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M2/A2: Exit the M2 at Junction 7 and take the A2 to Dover.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive directly into Dover and the Whitfield Roundabout where McDonalds is located.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take the 4th exit onto the A256/Whitfield Hill.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take the 1st exit off the next roundabout onto the A256/London Road.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Stay on this road, passing the 1st set of traffic lights at Crabble, and continue to the bottom of the road where you will find a 2nd set of lights adjacent to Hollis Motors.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Carry straight on at these lights, which will bring you into Buckland Avenue.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Carry straight on, then at the 3rd set of traffic lights turn right into Cherry Tree Avenue.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the next set of lights turn right and then take the 1st left into Coombe Valley Road.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Continue to the next roundabout and take the 1st exit onto the Poulton Close Industrial Estate.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Continue for a short distance and the Relyon Ferry Parking is on the right just past Coombes Kitchen Cafe.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Please allow at least 45 minutes for check in at the car park and transfer to the port. At peak periods additional time should be allowed.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Please arrive at the Car Park at least 45 minutes before you are due to check in at the Port. Customers are asked to drive direct to the compound and report to Reception. A member of Relyon staff will book your car in. You will then be asked to unload your luggage; we are more than willing to lend a hand if needed. When you have everything you need out of your car please hand in your car key to Reception. A Relyon bus driver will help you and your luggage into the Courtesy shuttle bus. We will also park your car for you.Drive direct to the car park and check-in at the office quoting your booking reference number.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>On your return you will need to call 01304 201227 for the Courtesy Shuttle bus to take you to the car park, which will arrive outside the Travel Centre, (just by the yellow AA information office) Please call when you are docked and just getting of the ferry. We will collect you from just outside the Yellow AA Breakdown office, the same place we dropped you off.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>01304 201227 Fax:01304 240289</helpline><distanceToAirport>Conveniently located just 3&amp;frac12; miles from Dover Port.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Relyon Parking operate transfers to and from Dover Port on demand. Please allow 45 minutes for checking in and transfer to the port.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>10 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Vehicles are stored in a fully fenced secure compound with CCTV, that is manned 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/DOVA.jpg</logoURL></carPark></carParks></airport><airport code=\"EMA\"><name>East Midlands Airport</name><shortname>eastmidlandsairport</shortname><terminals><terminal>1</terminal></terminals><carParks><carPark><code>EMAN</code><airport>EMA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>EAST MIDLANDS JETPARKS 1</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Free bus every 15 minutes&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Best value for money.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;On airport self car park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Keep your keys.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Ideal if you're looking for cheap airport parking.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Free bus transfer direct to the terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Operates Automatic Number Plate Recognition system (ANPR) &lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>East Midlands Airport, Castle Donington, Derby, DE74 2SA</address><directions>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M1 North: Exit at Junction 24.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take the A453 to East Midlands Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Turn right into the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the signs for JetParks 1.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M1 South: Exit at Junction 23a.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the signs for the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Turn right into the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the signs for JetParks 1.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;After leaving the M1 follow the A453 for 2.8 miles going past the airport until you reach a roundabout, turn right and after a few &amp;nbsp;hundred yards reach the final roundabout with JetParks&amp;nbsp;1 car park on your left.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;Alternatively, on arrival at the Airport main entrance, turn left at the roundabout and then follow signs to JetParks 1.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On arrival at the car park:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Drive up to the entrance barrier&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The Automatic Number Plate Recognition system (ANPR) will read your vehicle number plate, verify this against your booking details and the barrier should then open automatically. Please note, this process may take up to 30 to 40 seconds to happen &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If for any reason the barrier does not open after this time, please press the Assistance button and a member of staff will confirm your booking details with you and subsequently open the barrier to allow you entry&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Please DO NOT&amp;nbsp;press for a ticket to gain access to the car park, as this is not required and doing so will disable the ANPR system in relation to your booking&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On exiting the car park:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Proceed straight to the exit barrier and stop&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The ANPR system will read your vehicles number plate, verify this against your booking details and the barrier should then open automatically. Please note, this process may take up to 30 to 40 seconds to happen &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If for any reason the barrier does not open after this time, please press the Assistance button and a member of staff will confirm your booking details with you and subsequently open the barrier to allow you exit&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Please DO NOT&amp;nbsp;in any circumstance insert your credit card or debit card into the barrier as a further payment will be taken&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; East Midlands Long Stay Car Park 1Saver is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>08713 103300</helpline><distanceToAirport>East Midlands JetParks 1 is located within the airport perimeter and is an 8 minute bus journey from the Terminal.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Courtesy transfer buses leave JetParks 1 every 15 minutes with a journey time of 8 minutes to &amp;amp; from the terminal.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>8 Minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; East Midlands Long Stay Car Park 1 Saver is an on airport car park which has CCTV and holds the 'Park Mark' safer parking award.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>There is a maximum vehicle height of 3.0 metres (9 feet 10 inches) at this car park.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>All the shuttle buses are DDA compliant.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EMAN.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>EMAO</code><airport>EMA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>EAST MIDLANDS JETPARKS 2</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Guaranteed lowest onsite car park prices.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Free shuttle bus 24/7&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Guaranteed lowest onsite car park price.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Free shuttle bus 24/7.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;8 minutes transfer.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><a