;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On arrival at East Midlands Airport follow the signs for the Short Stay Car Par, take the middle lane signed Short Stay Car Park and Meet and Greet&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; At the entry barrier press the ticket request button and take a ticket&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Drive straight ahead, then bear slightly left following signs for Pre-Booked Meet and Greet&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; After approx. 15 metres you will see another barrier (on your right) where you will be met by a member of the Meet and Greet Team who will direct you where to park and where to check in&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On your return, please go to the Meet &amp;amp; Greet reception where a member of the Car Parks team will check your vehicle keys out to you and direct you to where your vehicle has been parked.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;pound;1.00 coin to exit the car park at the toll booth.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; East Midlands Long Stay Car Park 1Saver is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>08713 103300</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; The Short Stay Car Park is located less than a 2 minute walk from the terminal building. Your car will be moved to one of the East Midlands on-airport car parks for storage.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers are not required with this service as you will leave your car at the Short Stay Car Park and our valet staff will park your car for you.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; East Midlands Long Stay Car Park 1 Saver is an on airport car park which has CCTV and holds the 'Park Mark' safer parking award.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>There is a maximum vehicle height of 3.0 metres (9 feet 10 inches) at this car park.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>All the shuttle buses are DDA compliant.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EMAQ.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>EMAM</code><airport>EMA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>EAST MIDLANDS SHORT STAY CAR PARK</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Located directly in front of the Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Simply park and take the short walk to the check-ins.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Quick and convenient &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;car park is located directly in front of the Terminal&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Hassle-free &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>East Midlands Airport, Castle Donington, Derby, DE74 2SA</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M1 North: Exit at Junction 24.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the A453 to East Midlands Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Turn right into the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for the Short Stay Car Park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Please take the left or middle barriered lane for entry into the Short Stay Car Park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M1 South: Exit at Junction 23a.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Turn right into the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for the Short Stay Car Park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Please take the left or middle barriered lane for entry into the Short Stay Car Park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On arrival at the car park:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Drive up to the entrance barrier&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The Automatic Number Plate Recognition system (ANPR) will read your vehicle number plate, verify this against your booking details and the barrier should then open automatically. Please note, this process may take up to 30 to 40 seconds to happen &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If for any reason the barrier does not open after this time, please press the Assistance button and a member of staff will confirm your booking details with you and subsequently open the barrier to allow you entry&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Please DO NOT&amp;nbsp;press for a ticket to gain access to the car park, as this is not required and doing so will disable the ANPR system in relation to your booking&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On exiting the car park:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Proceed straight to the exit barrier and stop&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The ANPR system will read your vehicles number plate, verify this against your booking details and the barrier should then open automatically. Please note, this process may take up to 30 to 40 seconds to happen &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If for any reason the barrier does not open after this time, please press the Assistance button and a member of staff will confirm your booking details with you and subsequently open the barrier to allow you exit&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Please DO NOT&amp;nbsp;in any circumstance insert your credit card or debit card into the barrier as a further payment will be taken&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; East Midlands Long Stay Car Park 1Saver is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>08713 103300</helpline><distanceToAirport>East Midlands Short Stay Car Park is located directly in front of the terminal building.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this car park as it is less than a 2 minute walk from the Terminal.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; East Midlands Long Stay Car Park 1 Saver is an on airport car park which has CCTV and holds the 'Park Mark' safer parking award.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>There is a maximum vehicle height of 3.0 metres (9 feet 10 inches) at this car park.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>All the shuttle buses are DDA compliant.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EMAM.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>EMAI</code><airport>EMA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>EXPRESS PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Located next to the Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Convenient if you like to park and go.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Within walking distance to terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Convenient Park &amp;amp; Go.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Operates The Automatic Number Plate Recognition system.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>East Midlands Airport, Castle Donington, Derby, DE74 2SA</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M1 North: Exit at Junction 24.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the A453 to East Midlands Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Turn right into the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for Express Park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M1 South: Exit at Junction 23a.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Turn right into the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for Express Park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Drive up to the entrance barrier&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The Automatic Number Plate Recognition system will read your vehicle number plate , verify this against your booking details and the barrier should then open automatically. Please note this process may take &amp;nbsp;up to 30 to 40 seconds to happen &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If for any reason the barrier does not open after this time , Please press the Assistance button and a member of staff will confirm your&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; booking details with you and subsequently open the barrier to allow you entry&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Please DO NOT press for a ticket to gain access to the car park, as this is not required and doing so will disable the ANPR system&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; in relation to your booking.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Proceed straight to the exit barrier and stop. The ANPR system will read your vehicle number plate, verify this against your booking&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; details and the barrier should then open automatically.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; East Midlands Long Stay Car Park 1Saver is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>08713 103300</helpline><distanceToAirport>Express Parking is located adjacent to the terminal building.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this car park as it is just a 3 - 5 minute walk from the Departures Hall.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; East Midlands Long Stay Car Park 1 Saver is an on airport car park which has CCTV and holds the 'Park Mark' safer parking award.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>There is a maximum vehicle height of 3.0 metres (9 feet 10 inches) at this car park.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>All the shuttle buses are DDA compliant.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EMAI.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>EMAU</code><airport>EMA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>EXPRESS PARKING SAVER</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Located next to the Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Convenient if you like to park and go.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;BOOKINGS CAN NOT BE AMENDED OR REFUNDED WITH THIS PARKING SERVICE&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation></furtherInformation><address>East Midlands Airport, Castle Donington, Derby, DE74 2SA</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M1 North: Exit at Junction 24.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the A453 to East Midlands Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Turn right into the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for Express Park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M1 South: Exit at Junction 23a.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Turn right into the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for Express Park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Drive up to the entrance barrier&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The Automatic Number Plate Recognition system will read your vehicle number plate , verify this against your booking details and&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; the barrier should then open automatically. Please note this process may take &amp;nbsp;up to 30 to 40 seconds to happen&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If for any reason the barrier does not open after this time , Please press the Assistance button and a member of staff will confirm your&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; booking details with you and subsequently open the barrier to allow you entry&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Please DO NOT press for a ticket to gain access to the car park, as this is not required and doing so will disable the ANPR system&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; in relation to your booking.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Proceed straight to the exit barrier and stop. The ANPR system will read your vehicle number plate, verify this against your booking&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; details and the barrier should then open automatically.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; East Midlands Long Stay Car Park 1Saver is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>08713 103300</helpline><distanceToAirport>Express Parking is located adjacent to the terminal building.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this car park as it is just a 3 - 5 minute walk from the Departures Hall.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; East Midlands Long Stay Car Park 1 Saver is an on airport car park which has CCTV and holds the 'Park Mark' safer parking award.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>There is a maximum vehicle height of 3.0 metres (9 feet 10 inches) at this car park.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>All the shuttle buses are DDA compliant.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EMAU.jpg</logoURL></carPark></carParks></airport><airport code=\"EDI\"><name>Edinburgh Airport</name><shortname>edinburghairport</shortname><terminals><terminal>1</terminal></terminals><carParks><carPark><code>EDIK</code><airport>EDI</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>EDI PARKING - VALET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;The ultimate in speed and convenience.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Drop your keys off at the Terminal door and walk in.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Flexible booking.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Ultimate in speed and convenience.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Drop your keys off at the terminal door walk in.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Flexible booking&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; EDI Parking - Valet, Edinburgh Airport, Edinburgh EH12 9DN&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Follow the signs for Edinburgh Airport. When you get to the roundabout with the Hilton Hotel, continue straight ahead following Valet signs. Enter the Green Lane on the left, for authorised vehicles. Use the right hand Valet Barrier and drive into the Valet Parking Area outside the Terminal Building where your chauffeur will meet you. The chauffeur will check over your car and go through some paperwork with you, before taking your keys and driving your car to the car park.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; On return they will track your flight number and ensure that your car is waiting for you outside the Terminal Building when you land. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Drive up to the entry barrier and make your way to the Valet Parking area outside the Terminal building.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On your return the car park will track your flight and ensure your car is waiting for you outside the Terminal Building.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0844 448 8833&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; No need for transfer as the chauffeur will meet you at the terminal.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; All Edinburgh Airport's car parks are covered by CCTV and patrolled by 24 hour security teams. The Terminal Surface car park has the Park Mark accreditation so you can be confident your car will be safe whilst you are away.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EDIK.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>EDII</code><airport>EDI</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>EDI PARKING LONG STAY</name><description>&lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Official Long Stay Car Park for Edinburgh Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Park your car and keep your keys.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Only a 2 minute transfer to the Airport.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Park your car and keep your keys.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Only 2 mins transfer.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Number plate recognition.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; EDI Parking Long Stay, Gogar Bridge Road, Edinburgh Airport, Edinburgh EH12 9DN&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; The Long Stay Car park is located on-site. Turn right when you get to the Hlton Hotel roundabout, drive over the Tram crossing and take a right at the next roundabout. You wil see the Long Stay Car park entrance on your left hand side.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Please note: Do not drive into the NCP Scotpark - this car park is not operated by Edinburgh Airport.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; At the entry barrier press the intercom button on the ticket machine. The system will validate your booking and print a ticket. After you have parked make a note of the Zone and catch the free bus from your nearest bus stop. Please ensure you retain your ticket as this enables you to exit the car park on your return.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; To exit the the car park, drive up to the barrier and insert your ticket. The system will check your details and the barrier will open.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Upon arrival at the car park barrier, once your number plate is recognised, you will be issued with a ticket.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On your return the shuttle bus will collect you from the bus stand outside the Terminal Building.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0844 448 8833&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; A courtesy bus will take you to and from the airport.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>2 minutes by courtesy bus</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; All Edinburgh Airport's car parks are covered by CCTV and patrolled by 24 hour security teams. The Terminal Surface car park has the Park Mark accreditation so you can be confident your car will be safe whilst you are away.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>12</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EDII.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>EDIJ</code><airport>EDI</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>EDI PARKING TERMINAL SURFACE</name><description>&lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Surface Parking at the front of the Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;No bus needed and quick exit from the car park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;A short walk to the check-in area.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;No bus required.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Quick exit from the car park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;1 min walk to and from terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; EDI Parking Terminal Surface , Gogar Bridge Road, Edinburgh Airport, EH12 9DN&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; The Terminal Car Park is located on-site so please follow signs for Edinburgh Airport. On arrival at Edinburgh Airport please follow signs for the Short Stay Car Park. Your booking is valid for the Surface Car Park. At the entry barrier your registration number will be recognised. A ticket will be printed showing your registration and booking details. The barrier will open, If you have any difficulties, please press the call button for assistance. After parking make a note of what Zone you are in to help on your return.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Upon arrival at the car park barrier, once your number plate is recognised, you will be issued with a ticket.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Once you land, return to where you parked your vehicle and drive up to the exit barrier. The barrier will automatically open for you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0844 448 8833&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers are not required for this service. The car park is a 1 minute walk away from the Terminal Building.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>1 minute walk from the Terminal Building</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; All Edinburgh Airport's car parks are covered by CCTV and patrolled by 24 hour security teams. The Terminal Surface car park has the Park Mark accreditation so you can be confident your car will be safe whilst you are away.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EDIJ.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>EDIF</code><airport>EDI</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>FLYING SCOT EDINBURGH - PARK AND RIDE</name><description>&lt;li&gt;This is a convenient Park and Ride service located just on the outskirts of Edinburgh Airport, secure low-cost parking for Edinburgh Airport.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Excellent 24 hour service.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Fully secure parking.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;3-2 minutes from terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Flying Scot Edinburgh ,13 Fairview Road,&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Ingleston, Edinburgh EH28 8NB&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the A8 towards Edinburgh Airport: At the roundabout, follow signs for the terminal building (East Field Road) At the 2nd roundabout you will see the Hilton Hotel on the right hand side. Take the 1st left into Fair View. The car park is 400 yards along Fair View on the right hand side.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; **Please note do not enter the ''Scot Park'' this is not the car park you are booked into - you must go to Flying Scot Parking.**&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; IMPORTANT: Please arrive 30 minutes prior to check in. You will be required to leave your keys with the attendant. This car park will not except any vans - if you book and turn up with a van you will be turned away.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>On arrival at the car park, please check in at Reception where you will be given a receipt in exchange for your car keys.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>On your return, please use the white phones in the baggage collection area. Please dial *6135 to advise us that you have landed.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Low Cost Parking - Park &amp;amp; Ride is open every day of the year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0131 333 3445&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>The car park is located just 500 yards from the Terminal Building.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers to and from the terminal take approximately 10 minutes&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>2 - 3 Minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; While you're away, your car will be stored in a secured compound surrounded by an electric fence. Floodlighting and CCTV are in use and you need to enter a security code to exit the car park.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>96</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EDIF.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>EDIN</code><airport>EDI</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>LOW COST PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;High quality - Low cost!.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Just over 6 minutes from the Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Park outside reception then jump on the bus to the Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Low cost parking.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;High quality.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;6 mins to and from terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Park outside and jump on the bus.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Low Cost Parking&lt;br /&gt; 18 Queen Anne Drive,Ratho Station&lt;br /&gt; Glasgow Road&lt;br /&gt; Edinburgh&lt;br /&gt; EH28 8PL&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Leave the M9 at junction 1, taking the Newbridge exit at the roundabout, signposted for the B7030. Take the first left onto Cliftonhall Road passing McDonalds. Take another left onto Harvest Road. Pass under the bridge and take one more left onto Harvest Drive, entering Ratho Industrial Estate. Follow the road round and take the first left onto Queen Anne Drive. Pass the Newbridge bond and you will find the car park straight ahead.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On arrival please park in one of the bays outside reception and head inside to check your car in. Show your booking confirmation and hand in your keys. You will be given a a receipt and you car will be parked for you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Please arrive at the car park at least 30 minutes before your earliest recommended check-in time.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On return, there's a courtesy phone in arrivals you should use to call the bus. Dial 6314 and give your name and details, then wait at stop 11. Please show the receipt you were given at the car park to the bus driver when the bus arrives and they will take you back to the reception where your car will be waiting. &lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Low Cost Parking - Park &amp;amp; Ride is open every day of the year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0131 333 0091&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; Car park is located 5 to 10 minutes from Edinburgh airport and shuttle buses operate every 15 minutes, day and night.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers to and from the terminal take approximately 10-15 minutes&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>10 -15 Minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; While you're away, your car will be stored in a secured compound surrounded by an electric fence. Floodlighting and CCTV are in use and you need to enter a security code to exit the car park.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>96</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EDIN.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>EDIM</code><airport>EDI</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>PLANE PARKING MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Drop off and collect you car from the Multi-storey car park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;No bus needed and quick exit from the car park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Quick and convenient service.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Multi-storey car park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Drop and collect at Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;No buses needed.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Quick exit from car park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Plane Parking, Gogar Bridge Road, Edinburgh Airport, EH12 9DN&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Follow the signs to Edinburgh Airport. When you reach the roundabout next to the Hilton Hotel, continue straight ahead. At the next roundabout, drive straight ahead following the signs for the Terminal car park.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; When you get the barrier, please press the intercom and state you are a Plane Parking meet and greet customer. Drive into the Pick-up Zone, located on the ground floor of the multi-storey car park, where there is a clearly marked Plane Parking Meet and Greet area.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Return instructions will be issued on arrival at the Terminal.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>0844 770 3040</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers are not required for this service. The car park is outside the Terminal Building.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>Transfer are not required for this service.</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; All Edinburgh Airport's car parks are covered by CCTV and patrolled by 24 hour security teams. The Terminal Surface car park has the Park Mark accreditation so you can be confident your car will be safe whilst you are away.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>48</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EDIM.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>EDIH</code><airport>EDI</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>SECURE AIR PARKS - EARLY BIRD</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Secure parking located adjacent to the airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Automated check-in/check-out for quick and efficient service.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Extra savings for non-flexible bookings.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Secure parking.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Automated Check-in/Check-out.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Extra saving - Non-flexible booking&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Camera Recognition System in operation.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>100 Ingliston Road, Ingliston, Edinburgh, EH28 8AU</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;Camera Recognition System in operation. Please ensure that we have the correct car registration number.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the Forth road bridge: Follow the signs to the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the Newbridge Roundabout carry on following the signs to the airport along the A8.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;After 1&amp;frac14; miles turn left onto Ingliston Road&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow Ingliston Road to Secure Air Parks.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M8: Head for the Newbridge Roundabout (Junction 2).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the Newbridge Roundabout carry on following the signs to the airport along the A8.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;After 1&amp;frac14; miles turn left onto Ingliston Road&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow Ingliston Road to Secure Air Parks.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Camera Recognition System in operation. On arrival, drive up to the touch screen kiosk at the entrance barrier. If your details are not displayed on the screen, select option - I HAVE A BOOKING - and enter your booking reference number. Print a ticket, park in the nearest space and go to the bus stop where you will be picked up and taken to the airport.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Your entrance ticket will have the phone number for you to call when you return. After calling Secure Airparks make your way to Bus Stance 10 where you will be picked up and taken back to the car park.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0131 333 3377</helpline><distanceToAirport>The car park is 1 mile away from the airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Secure Air Parks operate transfers to and from the airport every 5 - 10 minutes which take just 1 minute.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>1 minute</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>All cars are parked in our fully insured &amp;quot;secured car park&amp;quot; which has CCTV and a Park Mark Award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EDIH.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>EDIC</code><airport>EDI</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>SECURE AIR PARKS - SELF PARK</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Secure parking located adjacent to the airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Automated check-in/check-out for quick and efficient service.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Secure parking.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Automated check-in/check-out service.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Quick and Efficient&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Camera Recognition System in operation. &lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>100 Ingliston Road, Ingliston, Edinburgh, EH28 8NB</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;Camera Recognition System in operation. Please ensure that we have the correct car registration number.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the Forth road bridge: Follow the signs to the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the Newbridge Roundabout carry on following the signs to the airport along the A8.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;After 1&amp;frac14; miles turn left onto Ingliston Road&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow Ingliston Road to Secure Air Parks.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M8: Head for the Newbridge Roundabout (Junction 2).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the Newbridge Roundabout carry on following the signs to the airport along the A8.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;After 1&amp;frac14; miles turn left onto Ingliston Road&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow Ingliston Road to Secure Air Parks.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Camera Recognition System in operation. On arrival, drive up to the touch screen kiosk at the entrance barrier. If your details are not displayed on the screen, select option - I HAVE A BOOKING - and enter your booking reference number. Print a ticket, park in the nearest space and go to the bus stop where you will be picked up and taken to the airport.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Your entrance ticket will have the phone number for you to call when you return. After calling Secure Airparks make your way to Bus Stance 10 where you will be picked up and taken back to the car park.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0131 333 3377</helpline><distanceToAirport>The car park is 1 mile away from the airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Secure Air Parks operate transfers to and from the airport every 5 - 10 minutes which take just 1 minute.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>1 minute</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>All cars are parked in our fully insured &amp;quot;secured car park&amp;quot; which has CCTV and a Park Mark Award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EDIC.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>EDIL</code><airport>EDI</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>TERMINAL SURFACE ONLINE SPECIAL</name><description>&lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Surface Parking at the front of the Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;No bus needed and quick exit from the car park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;A short walk to the check-in area.&lt;/li&gt;Special Online rates</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;No buses required.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;1 minute walk.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; EDI Parking Terminal Surface Online Special ,&amp;nbsp; Edinburgh Airport, EH12 9DN&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; The Terminal Car Park is located on-site so please follow signs for Edinburgh Airport. On arrival at Edinburgh Airport please follow signs for the Short Stay Car Park. Your booking is valid for the Surface Car Park. At the entry barrier your registration number will be recognised. A ticket will be printed showing your registration and booking details. The barrier will open, If you have any difficulties, please press the call button for assistance. After parking make a note of what Zone you are in to help on your return.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &amp;nbsp;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Upon arrival at the car park barrier, once your number plate is recognised, you will be issued with a ticket.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Once you land, return to where you parked your vehicle and drive up to the exit barrier. The barrier will automatically open for you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0844 448 8833&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;br /&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers are not required for this service. The car park is a 1 minute walk away from the Terminal Building.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>1 minute walk from the Terminal Building</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; All Edinburgh Airport's car parks are covered by CCTV and patrolled by 24 hour security teams. The Terminal Surface car park has the Park Mark accreditation so you can be confident your car will be safe whilst you are away.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EDIL.jpg</logoURL></carPark></carParks></airport><airport code=\"EXT\"><name>Exeter Airport</name><shortname>exeterairport</shortname><terminals><terminal>1</terminal></terminals><carParks><carPark><code>EXTB</code><airport>EXT</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>FLYPARKS MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;No struggling with luggage on and off buses and no long walks.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Your car is collected and returned to you within 120 yards of the terminal building.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;No long walks&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;No struggling with luggage&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Car collected and returned to terminal&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;120 yards away from terminal building&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; The Fair Oak House, EX5 2BH.&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; When you are 20 minutes away from Exeter Airport please call Flyparks on 07912 944 527.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The entrance to our drop off area at Fair oak farm house is located next to entrance to the Car park no P3.&amp;nbsp; When you’ve passed through sets of pedestrian lights on B3184 take 2nd turn right. You can see green sign for Fair oak farm and green light.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Drive in and our driver will meet you there.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; When you are 20 minutes away from Exeter Airport please call Flyparks on 07912 944 527.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The entrance to our drop off area at Fair oak farm house is located next to entrance to the Car park no P3.&amp;nbsp; When you’ve passed through sets of pedestrian lights on B3184 take 2nd turn right. You can see green sign for Fair oak farm and green light.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Drive in and our driver will meet you there.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; When you collect your luggage please make you way back to Fair oak house car park (approximately 120 yards from the airport). Our driver will handle your keys and car back.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Grange Park &amp;amp; Fly is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>01392 363303 or 07912 944527</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; The Fair Oak House car park is approximately 120 yards away from the airport.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers are not required with this service.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Grange Park &amp;amp; Fly has a secure compound with CCTV cameras and is manned 24 hours a day.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>This service is not available for mobile homes, caravans, lorries or trailers.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/EXTB.jpg</logoURL></carPark></carParks></airport><airport code=\"GLA\"><name>Glasgow Airport</name><shortname>glasgowairport</shortname><terminals><terminal>1</terminal></terminals><carParks><carPark><code>GLAF</code><airport>GLA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>DIRECT PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Secure self-parking site just 3 minutes from the airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Transfer bus drops you directly outside International Arrivals.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Secure parking&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;3 Minutes from the Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Transfer drops you outside Terminal&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Operates Automatic Number Plate Recognition System (ANPR). &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; 55 West March Road, Paisley, PA3 1BF&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M8: Exit at Junction 29 and take the A726 towards Paisley.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Stay in the right hand lane on the dual carriageway and turn right at the 1st set of lights.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Go straight over the mini-roundabout and under the railway bridge.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Direct Parking is located approximately 100 yards on the left.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Drive up to the entry barrier. (Our ANPR system will recognize your car registration number and will open automatically). Drop off your passengers and luggage at the Pick-Up point and then park your vehicle at the first available space. Then make your way back to the Pick-Up point. The courtesy shuttle bus will take you and your luggage to the airport and drop you off at bus stance 5 outside International Arrivals. Please arrive at the car park 30-40 mins before your airline check-in desk opens, especially in the summer season.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Call 0141 840 1234 or use the Freephone adjacent to International Arrivals (Dial #6180 and select Option 2) to notify us of your return. Make your way to bus stop 5 outside International Arrivals and you will be collected and returned to the car park. On exit from the car park, the barrier will open automatically.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Open 24hrs, 7 days a week.</openingPeriods><helpline>0141 840 1234 Fax: 0141 840 1236</helpline><distanceToAirport>The car park is less than 1&amp;frac12; miles from the Airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Direct Parking operate transfers to and from the airport on demand which take just 3 minutes. Please arrive at the car park 30-40 mins before your airline check-in desk opens, especially in the summer season.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>3 Minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Direct Parking has high security fencing, CCTV, entry barriers, 24hr security guards and has been accredited the PARK MARK award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>No restrictions but 2 spaces are required for long wheel based vans and cars with trailers.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&amp;nbsp;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/GLAF.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>GLAJ</code><airport>GLA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>FLYING SCOT GLASGOW - PARK AND RIDE</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Secure low-cost parking for Glasgow Airport.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Secure parking.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Low-cost.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;3 minutes from the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;CCTV.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Electric fencing barriers.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Full tarmac surface.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Glasgow Airport, 65 Well Street, Paisley, PA1 2PZ</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;Please arrive at Flying Scot at least 20 minutes before your flight check-in time.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;From Glasgow: &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Take the M8 to Junction 29.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Keep in the middle lane when approaching Glasgow Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Exit at Junction 29 and take the A726 for Paisley.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Follow the A726 until you reach a T-Junction.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Turn right on to the B7050/Underwood Road.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;At the next roundabout take the 3rd exit on to Well Street.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Flying Scot is located on Well Street on the left hand side.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;From Greenock/Erskine Bridge: &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Take the M8 to Junction 29.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Exit at Junction 29 and take the A726 for Paisley.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Follow the A726 until you reach a T-Junction.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Turn right on to the B7050/Underwood Road.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;At the next roundabout take the 3rd exit on to Well Street.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Flying Scot is located on Well Street on the left hand side.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Please arrive at Flying Scot at least 20 minutes before your flight check-in time. On arrival at the car park, please park at Reception and hand over your car keys.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>On your return, your car will be ready for you in the Car Park Departure Area.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Flying Scot Glasgow - Park &amp;amp; Ride is open every day of the year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt;0141 848 6033&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;FAX: 0141 848 0982&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>The car park is located less than 3 miles from Glasgow Airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; The bus service will operate on a 15 minute shedule.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>Approx. 5 Minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park is secured with CCTV cameras, full fencing, automatic floodlights and 24 hour guard dog patrols.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&amp;nbsp;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&amp;nbsp;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/GLAJ.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>GLAP</code><airport>GLA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>LONG STAY</name><description>&lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Less than 5 minutes by courtesy bus transfer.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;On Airport open air car park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;If you pre-book, you are always guaranteed a space.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Less than 5 mins to the Airport&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;On Airport open air car park&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Pre-booking always guaranteed a space.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Glasgow Airport Long Stay&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Paisley&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; PA3 2AY&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Glasgow Airport Long Stay&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From M8 Eastbound (from West of Scotland). Leave the M8 at junction 29 following signs for Glasgow Airport then follow the one way system around Caledonia Way into Inchinnan Road (approximately 2 miles). From M8 Westbound (from Edinburgh, Glasgow, North of England). Leave the M8 at junction 28 follow signs to Long Term Parking along Sanderling Road into Inchinnan Road (approximately 1 mile). Postcode: PA3 2AY&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Number plate recongnition in operation. Please wait for automatic ticket. If no ticket is issued press for assistance.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; At the exit please insert your entry ticket for your booking to be validated.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; 365 days a year&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0345 050 7080&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; Hop on one of the fast and frequent transfer buses - they come at least once every ten minutes and whisk you to the terminal in less than five.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers run every 10-15 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>5 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; The Car Park is frequently patrolled, enclosed by security fencing and has CCTV.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&lt;p&gt; Trailers are not permitted.&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>2</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; There are parking bays for Blue Badge holders near the bus stops. The courtesy coaches are wheelchair accessible.&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/GLAP.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>GLAD</code><airport>GLA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>PARK 'N' FLY</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Secure self-parking site just 5 minutes from the airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Transfer bus drops you directly outside International Arrivals.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>Secure parking,5 Minutes from the airport,Tranfer drops outside Terminal</furtherInformation><address>MacDowall Street, Paisley, PA3 2NB</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M8 (Glasgow):&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Go past Junction 28 (Glasgow Airport) and stay in the middle lane.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit at Junction 29 and take the A726 to Paisley.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout take the 1st exit on to the A726.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;After approximately 1 mile turn right on to MacDowall Street. (Park N Fly).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The car park is located on the left at the end of the road.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M8 (Greenock/Erskine Bridge):&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit at Junction 29 and take the A726 to Paisley.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout take the 3rd exit on to the A726.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;After approximately 1 mile turn right on to MacDowall Street. (Park N Fly).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The car park is located on the left at the end of the road.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the A737 (Johnstone/Beith/Irvine):&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the exit signposted for Paisley/Greenock/Glasgow Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout take the 4th exit on to the A726.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;After approximately 1 mile turn right on to MacDowall Street. (Park N Fly).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The car park is located on the left at the end of the road.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Approach the entry barrier (the ANPR system will recognise your number plate and the barrier will automatically open). Park at the first available space and make your way to the Pick-Up point for your transfer to the airport.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>On your return to Glasgow Airport, call 0141 840 1000 and make your way to Bus stop 5 located directly outside Arrivals. The transfer bus will take you back to the car park and on exit from the car park, the barrier will open automatically.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Open 24hrs, 7 days a week.</openingPeriods><helpline>0141 840 1000</helpline><distanceToAirport>Park 'N' Fly is located approximately 2 miles from the airport terminal.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Park 'N' Fly operate transfers to and from the airport on demand which take just 5 minutes. Please arrive at the car park 30-40 mins before your airline check-in desk opens, especially in the summer season.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>5 Minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; The car park has CCTV and regular police patrols.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>No restrictions but 2 spaces are required for long wheel based vans and cars with trailers.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&amp;nbsp;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/GLAD.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>GLAQ</code><airport>GLA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>PARKFAST</name><description>&lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Regular bus transfers run on demand.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;5 minute transfers to the Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;CCTV and regular security patrols.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Regular bus transfer.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;5 minute transfer to terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;CCTV and Regular security patrols.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; 66 Murray Street,Paisley, PA3 1QT&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From West Bound&amp;nbsp; M8 (Glasgow):&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Go past Junction 28 (Glasgow Airport) and stay in the middle lane.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Exit at Junction 29 and take the A726 to Paisley.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the roundabout take the 1st exit on to the A726.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; After approximately 1 mile turn right on to Murray Street..&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; The car park is located on the right.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M8 (Greenock/Erskine Bridge):&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Exit at Junction 29 and take the 3rd exit on the roundabout sign posted Paisley A726.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; After approximately 1 mile turn right on to Murray Street.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; The car park is located on the right.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the A737 (Johnstone/Beith/Irvine)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; On the A737 take the exit signposted for Paisley/Greenock/ Glasgow Airport&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the roundabout take the 4th exit sign posted Paisley A726&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; After approximately 1 mile turn right on to Murray Street.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; The car park is located on the right.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Approach barrier (our system will recognise your number plate and automatically open).&lt;br /&gt; Drop off luggage and passengers at Pick Up Point.&lt;br /&gt; Park at first available space and make your way to Pick Up Point for transfer to Airport.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;Call 0141 280 6070 (option 2). Make your way to Bus Stop 5 located directly outside Arrivals.&lt;br /&gt; &amp;nbsp;On exit from the carpark, the barrier will open automatically.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Open 24hrs, 7 days a week.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0141 280 6070&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;br /&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; ParkFast operate transfers to and from the airport on demand which take just 5 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>5 Minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; The car park has CCTV and regular police patrols.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>No restrictions but 2 spaces are required for long wheel based vans and cars with trailers.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>48</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&amp;nbsp;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/GLAQ.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>GLAC</code><airport>GLA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>PARKSAFE</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Secure self-parking site just 5 minutes from the airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Transfer bus drops you directly outside International Arrivals.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Secure parking. &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;5 Minutes transfer to the Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Transfer drops outside Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>1 Burnbrae Drive, Linwood, Paisley, PA3 3BU</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M8 (Glasgow):&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit at Junction 28A (A737 Irvine).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Join the dual carriageway (A737) Irvine.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit after approx. 1 mile for Linwood (A761) and take the right hand lane of the slip road to the Linclave roundabout.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the 2nd exit on the roundabout for the Linwood Industrial Estate onto Burnbrae Road.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the next turning on the left onto Burnbrae Drive.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Parksafe is located 100 yards along on the left.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M8 (Greenock/Erskine Bridge):&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit at Junction 29 (A737 Irvine).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the 4th exit on the roundabout (A737 Irvine).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Join the dual carriageway (A737) Irvine.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit after approx. 1 mile for Linwood (A761) and take the right hand lane of the slip road to the Linclave roundabout.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the 2nd exit on the roundabout for the Linwood Industrial Estate onto Burnbrae Road.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the next turning on the left onto Burnbrae Drive.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Parksafe is located 100 yards along on the left.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the A737 (Johnstone/Beith/Irvine):&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit the A737 at Linwood.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the right hand lane on the slip road to the Linclave roundabout.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the 4th exit on the roundabout for the Linwood Industrial Estate onto Burnbrae Road.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the next turning on the left onto Burnbrae Drive.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Parksafe is located 100 yards along on the left.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Check-in at the booth and park in your pre allocated space. Go to the customer waiting room or the nearest bus shelter. You will be given a ticket with a telephone number on it to call on your return for collection. The courtesy shuttle bus will take you and your luggage to the airport and drop you off at bus stance 5 outside International Arrivals. Please arrive at the car park 30-40 mins before your airline check-in desk opens, especially in the summer season.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Either use the free phone in the baggage reclaim area or call the direct line number on your receipt. Make your way to bus stance 5 outside International Arrivals where you were dropped off and you will be collected and returned to the car park.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Open 24hrs, 7 days a week.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt;0141 848 7222&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Fax: 0141 626 1519&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>Parksafe is located approximately 3 miles from the airport terminal.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Parksafe operate transfers to and from the airport on demand which take just 5 minutes. Please arrive at the car park 30-40 mins before your airline check-in desk opens, especially in the summer season.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>5 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park has CCTV, security fencing, entry barriers, 24hr security guards and has been accredited the PARK MARK award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>No restrictions but 2 spaces are required for long wheel based vans and cars with trailers.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/GLAC.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>GLAO</code><airport>GLA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>PURPLE PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;3miles from the terminal, 24 hour transfers&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;This is a self park car park&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;3 miles from the terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;24 hour transfers.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;This is a self park car park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; 1 Burnbrae drive&lt;br /&gt; Linwood&lt;br /&gt; PA3 3BJ&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; From the M8 westbound:&lt;br /&gt; Leave the motorway immediately after the airport at junction 28A and take the A737 towards Irvine. Follow the road, which becomes a dual carriageway, and after about two miles take the exit for Linwood and the A761. Follow the slip road, which leads to the Linclive roundabout. Take the second exit off the roundabout into Burnbrae Road and Linwood industrial estate. Turn left into Burnbrae Drive. Purple Parking Glasgow is at the end of Burnbrae Drive on the right.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M8 eastbound:&lt;br /&gt; Leave the motorway at junction 29 and take the fourth exit off the roundabout onto the A737 towards Irvine. Follow the road, which becomes a dual carriageway, and after about two miles take the exit for Linwood and the A761. Follow the slip road, which leads to the Linclive roundabout. Take the second exit off the roundabout into Burnbrae Road and Linwood industrial estate. Turn left into Burnbrae Drive. Purple Parking Glasgow is at the end of Burnbrae Drive on the right.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Approach the barrier and the car park's system will recognise your number plate; the barrier will then open automatically. Drop the luggage and passengers off at the entrance, park at the first available space and make your way to the pick up point to be transferred to the airport.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On your return, please call the number printed in your confirmation email. Then make your way to the Bus Stop 5 located directly outside the Arrivals. When you exit the car park, the barrier will open automatically for you.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods></openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0141 280 7771&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers run on demand and take about 6 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>6 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Purple Parking &amp;nbsp;has high security fencing, CCTV, infra-red perimeter beams, guard dogs and is floodlit and under 24 hour surveillance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; Facilities for disabled are available please email or phone direct for more details.&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/GLAO.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>GLAN</code><airport>GLA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>SKYPORT GLASGOW</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Situated just 3 miles from the Airport Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Self Park&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;24 hour transfers&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;p&gt;&amp;middot;&amp;nbsp; Situated just 3 miles from the Airport Terminal. &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;middot;&amp;nbsp; Self Park.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;middot;&amp;nbsp; 24 hour transfers.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;middot;&amp;nbsp; Operates Automatic Number Plate Recognition System (ANPR).&lt;/p&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; 1 Burnbrae drive&lt;br /&gt; Linwood&lt;br /&gt; PA3 3BJ&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; From the M8 westbound:&lt;br /&gt; Leave the motorway immediately after the airport at junction 28A and take the A737 towards Irvine. Follow the road, which becomes a dual carriageway, and after about two miles take the exit for Linwood and the A761. Follow the slip road, which leads to the Linclive roundabout. Take the second exit off the roundabout into Burnbrae Road and Linwood industrial estate. Turn left into Burnbrae Drive. Skyport Glasgow is at the end of Burnbrae Drive on the right.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M8 eastbound:&lt;br /&gt; Leave the motorway at junction 29 and take the fourth exit off the roundabout onto the A737 towards Irvine. Follow the road, which becomes a dual carriageway, and after about two miles take the exit for Linwood and the A761. Follow the slip road, which leads to the Linclive roundabout. Take the second exit off the roundabout into Burnbrae Road and Linwood industrial estate. Turn left into Burnbrae Drive. Skyport Glasgow is at the end of Burnbrae Drive on the right.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Approach the barrier and the car park's system will recognise your number plate; the barrier will then open automatically. Drop the luggage and passengers off at the entrance, park at the first available space and make your way to the pick up point to be transferred to the airport.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On your return, please call the number printed in your confirmation email. Then make your way to the Bus Stop 5 located directly outside the Arrivals. When you exit the car park, the barrier will open automatically for you.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods></openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0141 280 7771&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>This carpark is about 6 minutes away from the airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers run on demand and take about 6 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>6 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Purple Parking &amp;nbsp;has high security fencing, CCTV, infra-red perimeter beams, guard dogs and is floodlit and under 24 hour surveillance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; Facilities for disabled are available please email or phone direct for more details.&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/GLAN.jpg</logoURL></carPark></carParks></airport><airport code=\"HUY\"><name>Humberside International Airport</name><shortname>humbersideinternationalairport</shortname><terminals><terminal>1</terminal></terminals><carParks/></airport><airport code=\"LBA\"><name>Leeds Bradford Airport</name><shortname>leedsbradfordairport</shortname><terminals><terminal>1</terminal></terminals><carParks><carPark><code>LBAD</code><airport>LBA</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>MEET AND GREET INDOOR</name><description>&lt;li&gt;You will be met at the Airport Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Your car will be parked in a secure car park only 700 yards away.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;On return we will be waiting outside the Terminal with your car.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;You will met at the Terminal&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Your car will be parked in our secure car park 700 yards away.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Return met outside the Terminal&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Leeds Car Parks Ltd&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Unit 1A&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Leeds and Bradford Industrial Esate&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Yeadon&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; West Yorkshire&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; LS19 7XS&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Drive to the terminal and go into the drop-off car park. Turn right at the first roundabout you come to as you enter the airport. Make sure you use the drop-off lane or you may be charged &amp;pound;6 for entry&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; You should call the car park on 0113 250 6669&amp;nbsp; or&amp;nbsp; 0113 250 6555 when you are about five minutes from the airport. Your driver will meet you in the drop-off and pick-up car park, which is right outside the terminal - just turn right at the first roundabout you come to within the airport complex. Your driver will be wearing a Leeds Car Parks uniform.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Once you've collected your luggage, just give the car park a call on 0113 250 6669 or 0113 250 6555. Your driver will bring your car back to the pick-up and drop-off car park.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>The car park is open 24hrs a day, 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0113 250 6669 or 0113 250 6555&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport></transferFromAirport><transferTime>Transfers not required.</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; The car park has an eight-foot-tall fence, gates, CCTV cameras, barriers, floodlighting, staff on-site 24 hours a day and the Park Mark security award from the police.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&lt;p&gt; Caravans and motorhomes can't be parked undercover. Beyond that, there is no maximum car size.&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; This package is great for disabled customers as there are no transfers.&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LBAD.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LBAC</code><airport>LBA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>PARK AND RIDE INDOOR</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Only Indoor car park at Leeds Bradford Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Off-site car for Leeds Bradford Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Park mark security awarded car park.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>In-door car park,2 Minutes away from the Terminal,Park Mark secruity awarded car park</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Leeds Car Parks Ltd&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Unit 1A&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Leeds and Bradford Industrial Esate&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Yeadon&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; West Yorkshire&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; LS19 7XS&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; From the A658 southbound:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; Follow signs for the airport. Just before you get to it you will see Leeds and Bradford Airport Industrial Estate on your left hand side, opposite Leeds Helijet. Please go through security gate 2, which is the first entrance you come to.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the A658 northbound:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; Follow signs for the airport. Once you've gone under the airport runway, go straight on at the roundabout which is the second exit towards Harrogate. You will then see Leeds and Bradford Airport Industrial Estate on your right hand side. When you drive into the industrial estate go through security gate 2, opposite Leeds Helijet.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; If you're using a Sat Nav please use this postcode: LS19 7WP.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; When you arrive, you'll need to show your booking confirmation to the member of staff at the gate. Then just drive in - the barrier will be opened for you too - and head to the reception desk, where you'll need to check in and hand in your keys. Your car will be parked for you. Then all you have to do is jump on the minibus to the airport.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Once you're back in Blighty, and have collected your luggage, call 0113 250 6669 and Leeds Car Parks will send a minibus to come and collect you. It may be the only easy thing about coming back from holiday. Then just go to reception with your booking confirmation and pick up your keys. A member of staff will open the barrier and the gates to let you out.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>The car park is open 24hrs a day, 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0113 250 6669 or&amp;nbsp; 0113 250 6555&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; The Airport is 2 minutes away from the car park.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Airport transfers run on demand, 24 hours a day, and takes just two minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>2 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; The car park has an eight-foot-tall fence, gates, CCTV cameras, barriers, floodlighting, staff on-site 24 hours a day and the Park Mark security award from the police.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&lt;p&gt; Caravans and motorhomes can't be parked undercover. Beyond that, there is no maximum car size.&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; This package is great for disabled customers as there are no transfers.&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LBAC.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LBAB</code><airport>LBA</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>PARK AND RIDE OUTDOOR</name><description>&lt;li&gt;2 minutes from the Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Off-site car for Leeds Bradford Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&