ooking via the call centre; 0845 319 0421.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; Disabled parking spaces are located at the front of the car parks (Long Stay, Premium, and Multi-Storey), they are subject to availability.&amp;nbsp; Iparkliverpool customers requiring disabled parking should go to the Long Stay Car Park. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LPLQ.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LPLK</code><airport>LPL</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>LIVERPOOL LONG STAY</name><description>&lt;li&gt;On Airport, Safe, Secure &amp;amp; Convenient.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Within walking distance of the terminal building.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;On Airport, Safe, Secure and Convenient.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Within walking distance.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Operates Automatic Number Plate Recognition System (ANPR)&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Liverpool John Lennon Airport, L24 1YD</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the North/North-East: Take the M6 to Junction 21A with the M62.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Please note that Junction 21A is a split junction, and motorists should ensure they come off at the slip road signposted Liverpool.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow M62 westbound to Junction 6 and onto the A5300.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the A5300 onto the A561 and follow the signs to Liverpool John Lennon Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The 'Long Stay Car Park' can be accessed by turning left on the roundabout when approaching the airport terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the South/East: Take the M6 to Junction 20 with the M56.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow M56 to Junction 12 and onto the A557/A562 dual carriageway via Runcorn Bridge to merge with A561.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs to Liverpool John Lennon Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The 'Long Stay Car Park' can be accessed by turning left on the roundabout when approaching the airport terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the Wirral/North Wales: Passengers travelling from the Wirral may find it more convenient at peak times to use the M53 and then the M56 rather than a route through the City Centre of Liverpool via the Mersey Tunnels.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Passengers travelling from North Wales should join the A55 to connect with the M56 eastbound.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow M56 to Junction 12 and onto the A557/A562 dual carriageway via Runcorn Bridge to merge with A561.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs to Liverpool John Lennon Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The 'Long Stay Car Park' can be accessed by turning left on the roundabout when approaching the airport terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Drive up to the entry barrier, the ANPR system will read your vehicle registration number and automatically issue you with a ticket, your pre-booked reference number and vehicle registration number will be printed on the ticket (please wait about 20 seconds for this process). Remove the ticket, and the barrier will rise allowing you to enter. Please retain the ticket and keep it safe as you will need this to exit. Should the system fail to recognise your vehicle or the barrier does not rise for you automatically when you arrive at the airport, please press the intercom for assistance. Please have your booking reference to hand.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Drive to the exit barrier and insert your car park ticket. The barrier will rise automatically allowing you to exit. If the system failed to recognise your vehicle on entry, before collecting your vehicle, take your ticket and a copy of your booking confirmation to the car park office (ground floor of the Multi-Storey car park), where your ticket will be validated for exit.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Liverpool Long Stay - Price Buster is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0844 871 7496</helpline><distanceToAirport>The Long Stay Car Park is located within the airport boundary, a short walking distance away from the terminal building.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required as the car park is just a short walk from the terminal.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Liverpool Long Stay - Price Buster is an official on-airport car park, managed by Peel Airports Ltd. They have high levels of security, with a high-tech CCTV system, electronically controlled entry and exit barriers, Automatic Number Plate Recognition, and 24 hour security patrols with a dedicated car park security team. All of the on-airport car parks at Liverpool John Lennon Airport hold the 'Park Mark' award for safer parking.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>There are no height restrictions at this car park, however please note that they do not allow trailers, or coaches. Any vehicles requiring more than one space must be booked via their call centre on 0844 871 7496.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>Disabled parking spaces are located at the front of the car park but are subject to availability.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LPLK.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LPLN</code><airport>LPL</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>LIVERPOOL LONG STAY - PRICE BUSTER</name><description>&lt;li&gt;On Airport, Safe, Secure &amp;amp; Convenient.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Within walking distance of the terminal building.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Extra savings for non-flexible bookings.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Safe, Secure &amp;amp; Convenient.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Within walking distance.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Extra savings - Non flexible booking.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Liverpool Airports Ltd. Liverpool John Lennon Airport, L24 1YD&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the North/North-East: Take the M6 to Junction 21A with the M62.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Please note that Junction 21A is a split junction, and motorists should ensure they come off at the slip road signposted Liverpool.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow M62 westbound to Junction 6 and onto the A5300.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the A5300 onto the A561 and follow the signs to Liverpool John Lennon Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The 'Long Stay - Price Buster Car Park' can be accessed by turning left on the roundabout when approaching the airport terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the South/East: Take the M6 to Junction 20 with the M56.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow M56 to Junction 12 and onto the A557/A562 dual carriageway via Runcorn Bridge to merge with A561.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs to Liverpool John Lennon Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The 'Long Stay - Price Buster Car Park' can be accessed by turning left on the roundabout when approaching the airport terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the Wirral/North Wales: Passengers travelling from the Wirral may find it more convenient at peak times to use the M53 and then the M56 rather than a route through the City Centre of Liverpool via the Mersey Tunnels.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Passengers travelling from North Wales should join the A55 to connect with the M56 eastbound.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow M56 to Junction 12 and onto the A557/A562 dual carriageway via Runcorn Bridge to merge with A561.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs to Liverpool John Lennon Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The 'Long Stay - Price Buster Car Park' can be accessed by turning left on the roundabout when approaching the airport terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Drive up to the entry barrier, the ANPR system will read your vehicle registration number and automatically issue you with a ticket, your pre-booked reference number and vehicle registration number will be printed on the ticket (please wait about 20 seconds for this process). Remove the ticket, and the barrier will rise allowing you to enter. Please retain the ticket and keep it safe as you will need this to exit. Should the system fail to recognise your vehicle or the barrier does not rise for you automatically when you arrive at the airport, please press the intercom for assistance. Please have your booking reference to hand.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Drive to the exit barrier and insert your car park ticket. The barrier will rise automatically allowing you to exit. If the system failed to recognise your vehicle on entry, before collecting your vehicle, take your ticket and a copy of your booking confirmation to the car park office (ground floor of the Multi-Storey car park), where your ticket will be validated for exit.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Liverpool Long Stay - Price Buster is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0844 871 7496</helpline><distanceToAirport>The Long Stay - Price Buster Car Park is located on-airport within a five minute walking distance from the terminal building.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required as the car park is within a five minute walk from the terminal.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></can