tem fail to recognise your vehicle or the barrier does not rise for you automatically when you arrive at the airport, please press the intercom for assistance. Please have your booking reference to hand.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Drive to the exit barrier and insert your car park ticket. The barrier will rise automatically allowing you to exit.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Liverpool Long Stay - Price Buster is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0844 871 7496</helpline><distanceToAirport>The Premium Car Park is located within the airport boundary, adjacent to the terminal building.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required as the car park is less than a 60 second walk from the terminal.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Liverpool Long Stay - Price Buster is an official on-airport car park, managed by Peel Airports Ltd. They have high levels of security, with a high-tech CCTV system, electronically controlled entry and exit barriers, Automatic Number Plate Recognition, and 24 hour security patrols with a dedicated car park security team. All of the on-airport car parks at Liverpool John Lennon Airport hold the 'Park Mark' award for safer parking.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>There are no height restrictions at this car park, however please note that they do not allow trailers, or coaches. Any vehicles requiring more than one space must be booked via their call centre on 0844 871 7496.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>Disabled parking spaces are located at the front of the car park but are subject to availability.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LPLM.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LPLF</code><airport>LPL</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>SKYPARK LIVERPOOL MEET AND GREET PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Convenient and time-saving parking service.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Convenient&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Time saving&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Meet and Greet&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;On departure and return&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Skypark Liverpool Meet &amp;amp; Greet, 22 Owens Drive, Speke Hall Avenue, Liverpool, L24 1YL.</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;PLEASE NOTE: Customers are required to contact the Chauffeur on the number provided 10 minutes before arrival to confirm the meeting time.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M6 (North): Exit at Junction 21a and take the M62 west to Junction 6.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit the M62 and take the A5300 and then the A561 and follow the signs to the airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M6 (South): Exit at Junction 20 and take the M56 west to Junction 12.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit the M56 and take the A557/A562 via Runcorn Bridge to merge with the A561.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Then follow the signs to the airport&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>PLEASE NOTE: Customers are required to contact the Chauffeur on the number provided 10 minutes before arrival to confirm the meeting time. The chauffeur will meet you in the airport's drop-off Short Stay Car Park at your arranged meeting time. All chauffeurs will be wearing full uniform.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Full details of the return procedure will be provided by your chauffeur on collection of your vehicle.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>APL Liverpool Outdoor is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>07918 056667</helpline><distanceToAirport>The car park is located 500 metres from the airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport></transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>APL Liverpool Parking has 24 hour security patrols; security/crash barriers; CCTV surveillance and full perimeter security fencing.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>Skypark Liverpool cannot accept the following vehicles: lorries; mobile homes; or commercial vehicles.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>APL Liverpool Parking has spacious and accessible disabled toilet facilities. The car park's staff will provide assistance where required.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LPLF.jpg</logoURL></carPark></carParks></airport><airport code=\"LCY\"><name>London City Airport</name><shortname>londoncityairport</shortname><terminals><terminal>1</terminal></terminals><carParks><carPark><code>LCYB</code><airport>LCY</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>SAPHIRE TRIO MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Convenient chauffeur parking service.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Convenient Chauffeur Service.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Meet you airport Terminal car park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Car stores 2 miles away.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Terminal car park, Hartman Road, London, E16 2PX&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; PLEASE CALL 07903 416577 WHEN YOU ARE 20 MINUTES AWAY FROM ARRIVING AT THE AIRPORT.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From Central London: Take the A13 eastwards out of London.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Turn right onto the A1261.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the junction with the A1020 take the 4th exit on the roundabout.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Carry on along the A1020 following the signs for the airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the East: Take the A13 towards London.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the junction with the A1020, take the 1st exit on the roundabout.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Carry on along the A1020 following the signs for the airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Please call 07903 416577 when you are 20 minutes from the airport. On arrival at the airport drive into the Terminal car park (Terminal Parking) and take a ticket. You will need to hand your keys along with your ticket to our driver. Please take all your valuables with you.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; An additional fee of &amp;pound;20 will be incurred if you are anything between 20-40 minutes late. If you fail to contact us after 40 minutes your booking will be automatically cancelled without refund.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; When you arrive back, please call 07903 416577 once you have landed. Our driver will meet you at the Terminal car park.(Terminal Parking)&amp;nbsp; You will be given a car park ticket. PLEASE NOTE: There is a &amp;pound;7.00 charge to exit the car park.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Saphire Trio Meet &amp;amp; Greet is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Please note that London City Airport opening hours on Sundays are 11am.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 07903 416577&lt;br /&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>Your car will be stored at our secure car park located 2 miles from London City Airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required as this is a meet and greet service. Your car is collected and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; The car park has 24 hour patrols and barrier entry.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LCYB.jpg</logoURL></carPark></carParks></airport><airport code=\"LGW\"><name>London Gatwick</name><shortname>londongatwick</shortname><terminals><terminal>N</terminal><terminal>S</terminal></terminals><carParks><carPark><code>LGWH</code><airport>LGW</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>APH MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Have your vehicle collected from &amp;amp; returned to you at the terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Excellent service from specialists with 30 years of Airport Parking experience.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt; Winners for the fourth year running of the Best Airport Parking category at the British Travel Awards.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Excellent service&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;30 years if Airport parking experience. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Winners for the Fourth year running of the Best Airport Parking.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Snow Hill, Copthorne, Crawley, Sussex, RH10 3EQ</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Please call 08448 717539 or 07793 267974 at least 30 minutes BEFORE arriving at the airport to confirm your arrival time. Please make your way to Gatwick Airport and follow these instructions for South and North Terminal Departures. APH will meet you in the SHORT STAY CAR PARK (Do not follow the signs for PASSENGER DROP OFF).&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &lt;br /&gt; FOR NORTH TERMINAL:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Please follow the signs for the North Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the signs for SHORT STAY - PASSENGER PICK-UP&amp;nbsp;into theSHORT TERM CAR PARK -&amp;nbsp;keep in the left lane&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take ticket at barrier (there will be nothing to pay)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive to CAR PARK 6 - last car park on right&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Proceed to LEVEL 1 &amp;nbsp;- Row D and E&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Park vehicle in - APPROVED OPERATOR BAYS. and unload luggage&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Lock your car and hand keys and car park ticket to chauffeur&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; You will be given your return instructions at this point&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &lt;br /&gt; FOR SOUTH TERMINAL:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Please follow signs for the South Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the signs for SHORT STAY - PASSENGER PICK-UP into theSHORT TERM CAR PARK&amp;nbsp;keep in the right hand lane&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take ticket at barrier (there will be nothing to pay)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive to 3rd car park&amp;nbsp;ORANGE CAR PARK 3&amp;nbsp;Level 1, Row D and E&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Park vehicle in - APPROVED OPERATOR BAYS. and unload luggage&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Lock vehicle and hand keys and car park ticket to chauffeur&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; You will be given your return instructions at this point&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Please call 08448 717539 or 07793 267974 at least 30 minutes BEFORE arriving at the airport to confirm your arrival time. The Chauffeur will meet you at the appropriate drop-off point and check your booking details and any vehicle damage before issuing you with instructions for your return. Please note we can only accept vehicles with a valid tax disc and in roadworthy condition.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Full return instructions will be provided by the chauffeur on arrival at the airport.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Car park operates 24 hours a day.</openingPeriods><helpline>08448 717539  &lt;br /&gt; 07793 267974</helpline><distanceToAirport>Your car will be stored at APH's secure car park, which is located 7 miles from the airport terminals.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected fro