auffeur will meet you at the terminal at the arranged time. Pleasae see your booking confirmation for precise details.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Full return instructions will be given to you on arrival at the airport.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 020 8813 8130&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; Your car will be parked in one of our secure car parks, located minutes away from London Heathrow Airport.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>n/a</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>24 hour security guards. CCTV. Purple Parking have been issued with a gold award by the police for security.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&lt;p&gt; Please note that all Heathrow Short Stay Car Parks have height limits.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 1 Short Stay Car Park 1 - 2.05m (6ft 9in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 2 Short Stay Car Park 2 - 2.05m (6ft 9in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 3 Short Stay Car Park 3 - 2.20m (7ft 2in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 4 Short Stay Car Park 4 - 2.00m (6ft 6in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 5 Short Stay Car Park 5 - 2.20m (7ft 2in)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; *Please take this into account if you have a roof luggage box installed on your vehicle*&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; This product is ideal for the disabled traveller.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LHRJ.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LHRO</code><airport>LHR</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>METEOR MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;NEW TO PURPLE PARKING!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Meteor Meet and Greet have been a leading providers of Heathrow meet and greet parking at all of Heathrow airport terminals for the past 15 years. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;Our Chauffeur driver meets you at the airport and delivers your car back to you on your return.  &lt;li&gt;Competitively priced - great service.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; MEETING POINTS ON ARRIVAL&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 2 - ARRIVAL INSTRUCTIONS&amp;nbsp;(Postcode for GPS to Terminal 2:&amp;nbsp;TW6 1EW)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Follow signs to the Short Stay Car Park 2&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Drive up the ramp, fork right and drive under the yellow height restriction arm&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Keep&amp;nbsp;to your left and stay in the lane for level 1, 2 &amp;amp; 3 (the car park entrance on your far left) (PLEASE DO NOT ENTER THE CAR PARK VIA THE FAR RIGHT HAND BARRIERS)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Drive down the ramp following the&amp;nbsp;P - Off Airport signs&amp;nbsp;and exit at level 2.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Follow the&amp;nbsp;P - Off Airport signs&amp;nbsp;all the way round until you reach Rows A and B at the far end of the car park.&amp;nbsp;Take your keys to the Purple Parking/Meteor Handover captain at the grey desk near the lifts.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 2 - RETURN INSTRUCTIONS &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Leave customs, turn left and exit the terminal opposite Travelex/M&amp;amp;S food, walk across the pedestrian bridge and take the set of lifts on the left to level 2 rows A and B.Collect your keys from our representative at the grey desk.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 3 - ARRIVAL INSTRUCTIONS&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;(Postcode for GPS to Terminal 3:&amp;nbsp;TW6 1QG)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the sign to the Short Stay Car Park 3&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive up the 