ellow height restriction arm&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; KEEP&amp;nbsp;to your&amp;nbsp;LEFT&amp;nbsp;and follow the signs&amp;nbsp;for&amp;nbsp;Short stay&amp;nbsp;Level 4.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Once inside, follow the arrows and the&amp;nbsp;P - Off Airport&amp;nbsp;signs to the end of the car park to ROWS R &amp;amp; S.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take your keys to the Purple Parking/Meteor Handover captain at the grey desk near the lifts.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 5 - RETURN INSTRUCTIONS&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Leave via the red exit past Caf&amp;eacute; Nero, when outside the building take the lift to level 4 Row S short stay car park and collect your keys from our representative at the grey desk.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Please note if the flight number is incorrect or you come on an earlier flight please call 0208 867 4618 otherwise your vehicle will not be dispatched.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; You will be met at your designated Terminal by one of our Chauffeur drivers. Precise arrival instructions will be given on your booking confirmaiton.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Full return instructions will be issued by the driver on collection of the vehicle. Please note that if your return flight into Heathrow is delayed beyond midnight, we reserve the right to pick you up at the terminal by courtesy bus and drive you to our car park to collect your vehicle.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 07956 471 302&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellatio