yment machine.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Please note&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Purple Parking has made special arrangements&amp;nbsp;with Heathrow Airport at all terminals for our customers to drop off their cars&amp;nbsp;on arrival&amp;nbsp;inside the Short Term Car Parks.&amp;nbsp;One of the Handover Captains will always be there from 05.00 to at least 22.00&amp;nbsp;7 days a week / 365 days a year.&amp;nbsp;No need to telephone if you are early or late for your arrival time&amp;nbsp;- the Captain will be there for you. No need for an umbrella - the meeting points are all undercover.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; PLEASE CALL 0845 450 0808 - 30 minutes prior to your pre-booked meet time. Our chauffeurs, who wear black jackets, will meet you at the terminal building at the arranged time.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Return instructions will be provided by your chauffeur on arrival.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0845 450 0808&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; Your car will be parked in one of our secure car parks, located minutes away from London Heathrow Airport.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>n/a</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>24 hour security guards. CCTV. Purple Parking have been issued with a gold award by the police for security.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&lt;p&gt; Please note that all Heathrow Short Stay Car Parks have height limits.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 1 Short Stay Car Park 1 - 2.05m (6ft 9in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 2 Short Stay Car Park 2 - 2.05m (6ft 9in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 3 Short Stay Car Park 3 - 2.20m (7ft 2in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 4 Short Stay Car Park 4 - 2.00m (6ft 6in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 5 Short Stay Car Park 5 - 2.20m (7ft 2in)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; *Please take this into account if you have a roof luggage box installed on your vehicle*&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; This product is ideal for the disabled traveller.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LHRK.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LHRZ</code><airport>LHR</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>NCP FLIGHTPATH 2-3</name><description>&lt;li&gt;This Car Park is only for Terminals 2-3.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Buses operate every 20 minutes.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Off Airport Car Park.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation></furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Heathrow Terminals 2-3 (Flightpath), Heathrow Flightpath, West Drayton, UB7 0DU&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Our postcode, should you need it for your Sat Nav system is&amp;nbsp;UB7 0DU.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; You should leave the M4 at Junction 4. Follow the signs for Terminals&amp;nbsp; 2&amp;nbsp;and 3, this will take you down the Heathrow Spur Road. Keep in the left lane and turn left at the traffic lights. Go up the hill and turn left just before the first set of traffic lights. On your left will be the Park Inn Hotel. Follow the signs around the side of the hotel. You’ll go over a bridge and you should turn left. The car park will be directly in front of you.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; To make your parking experience easier we now have&amp;nbsp;number plate recognition. If you have pre-booked a space you no longer need to push for a ticket. Our camera will read your number plate and issue you a ticket automatically.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Simply drive up to the&amp;nbsp;exit barrier, insert the ticket you were given at the entry barrier. The barrier will rise and you can leave the car park.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0345 050 7080&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; The car park is conveniently located 8-to-12 minutes away from the Airport.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; The car park offers frequent courtesy bus transfers to and from the airport which take 8-to-12 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>20 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park has CCTV, security fencing, 24-hour security guards, spike-strips on entrance and a controlled exit. The car park also has a 'Park Mark' safer parking award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>Height restriction at this car park of 2.15 m (7ft.) which include roof racks and roof boxes.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>4</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LHRZ.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LHRG</code><airport>LHR</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>PURPLE PARKING BUSINESS</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Multi-Storey and less than a mile from the airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;As convenient as any On-Airport car park but at an Off-Airport price.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Multi-storey car park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Less than a mile from airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Height restriction of 2.3m.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Quick journey.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; 17 Bath Road, Heathrow, Hounslow, Middlesex, TW6 2AL&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Important Information regarding our Business Parking Service&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; As the company cannot verify what items are left in your vehicle, we would kindly request that you remove any loose items such as&amp;nbsp;Sat Navs, loose cash, sunglasses etc&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; ___________________________________________________________________________&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M25&lt;br /&gt; - Leave the motorway at Junction 15 and follow the M4 signposted to London.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M4&lt;br /&gt; - Leave the motorway at Junction 3 and follow the A312 towards Hounslow / Feltham.&lt;br /&gt; - At the Jolly Waggoners roundabout turn right onto A4 (Bath Road) towards Heathrow.&lt;br /&gt; - Purple Parking Business is approximately 1 mile along the A4 on the left, next door to the Premier Inn Hotel.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>You will be directed to the arrivals area by a Purple Parking Business host.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Full details of the returns procedure will be given on arrival at the car park.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0845 450 0808</helpline><distanceToAirport>Located 5 minutes from the Airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>The car park offers frequent courtesy bus transfers to and from the airport which take 5 - 13 minutes.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>5 - 13 Minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park has CCTV, security fencing, 24-hour security guards, spike-strips on entrance and a controlled exit. The car park also has a 'Park Mark' safer parking award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>Height restriction at this car park of 2.15 m (7ft.) which include roof racks and roof boxes.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LHRG.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LHRW</code><airport>LHR</airport><serviceType>O</serviceType><name>PURPLE PARKING BUSINESS EXPRESS</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Our Handover Captain meets you at the airport on your departure.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;On your return you will be taken by minibus to our Long Stay car park where your car will be ready near our reception in our collection area.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>Meet on departure,Return to our Long stay car park,Save time on departure,Convenient</furtherInformation><address>169 Brent Road, Southall, Middlesex, UB2 5LE.</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; MEETING POINTS ON ARRIVAL&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The Handover Captains are at their desks from 05.00 every day. (From 04.30 at Terminal 2)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; IF YOU ARE RUNNING EARLY OR LATE, PLEASE CALL THE HELPLINE ON 0845 850 5859&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Important Information regarding our Meet &amp;amp; Greet Service&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; It is essential that you hand over your keys to our representative at the terminal, so that your vehicle can be moved to our car park. Purple Parking can not be held responsible for any car parking costs incurred, if we are not able to move your vehicle.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; As the company cannot verify what items are left in your vehicle, we would kindly request that you remove any loose items such as&amp;nbsp;Sat Navs, loose cash, sunglasses etc.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 1 - ARRIVAL INSTRUCTIONS&amp;nbsp; (Postcode for GPS to Terminal 1: TW6 1AP)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the signs to the Short Stay Car Park 1 (entrance on the ground floor - NOT Short Stay Car Park 1A upstairs)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the entrance barrier, take a ticket (there will be nothing to pay)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Keep to your right and&amp;nbsp;IMMEDIATELY TAKE A FIRST LEFT&amp;nbsp;down to the lower ground floor&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Turn right and drive all the way to the end and bear left after the portacabin (this is not our portacabin), until you are facing the opposite direction&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; You will see our Off Airport Meet &amp;amp; Greet parking bays immediately to your right&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Park your car in one of these bays&amp;nbsp;(PLEASE&amp;nbsp;do not park in Disabled, Brown Badge or Unpaid ticket bays, as Purple Parking will not be&amp;nbsp;responsible&amp;nbsp;for tickets issued by Heathrow Airport)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Lock your car and give the keys and parking ticket to the Handover Captain, who will be waiting for you&amp;nbsp;at his grey desk&amp;nbsp;near the payment machine.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 2 - Arrival Instructions&amp;nbsp;(Postcode for GPS to Terminal 2:&amp;nbsp;TW6 1EW)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Follow signs to the Short Stay “2&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Drive up the ramp, fork right and drive under the yellow height restriction arm&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Keep&amp;nbsp;to your left and stay in the lane for level 1, 2 &amp;amp; 3 (the car park entrance on your far left) (PLEASE DO NOT ENTER THE CAR PARK ON THE FAR RIGHT HAND BARRIERS)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;At the entrance barrier, take a ticket (there will be nothing to pay)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Drive down the ramp following the&amp;nbsp;P - Off Airport signs&amp;nbsp;and exit at level 2.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Follow the&amp;nbsp;P - Off Airport signs&amp;nbsp;all way round until you reach Rows A and B at the far end of the car park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;You will see our blue Off Airport Meet &amp;amp; Greet parking bays in&amp;nbsp;Row A (Bays 1 to 6) &amp;amp; Row B (Bays 1 - 14)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Park your car in one of these bays&amp;nbsp;(PLEASE&amp;nbsp;do not park in Disabled, Brown Badge or Unpaid ticket bays, as Purple &amp;nbsp;Parking will not be held&amp;nbsp;responsible&amp;nbsp;for tickets issued by Heathrow Airport)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Lock your car and give the keys and parking ticket to the Handover Captain, who will be waiting for you&amp;nbsp;at his grey desk&amp;nbsp;in the lift area near the payment machine.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 3 - ARRIVAL INSTRUCTIONS&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;(Postcode for GPS to Terminal 3: TW6 1QG)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the sign to the Short Stay Car Park 3&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the entrance barrier, take a ticket (there will be nothing to pay)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive up the ramp and exit at level 3&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the road all the way round until you reach Rows A and B at the far end of the Car Park (drive past the first lift area)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; You will see our Off Airport Meet &amp;amp; Greet parking bays opposite the lifts&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Park your car in one of these bays&amp;nbsp;(PLEASE do not park in Disabled, Brown Badge or Unpaid ticket bays, as Purple Parking will not be held&amp;nbsp;responsible&amp;nbsp;for tickets issued by Heathrow Airport)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Lock your car and give the keys and parking ticket to the Handover Captain, who will be waiting for you&amp;nbsp;at his grey desk&amp;nbsp;in the lift area near the payment machine.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 4 - ARRIVAL INSTRUCTIONS&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;(Postcode for GPS to Terminal 4: TW6 3XA)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the signs to short stay car park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive up the ramp and keep to your right&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the entrance barrier, take a ticket (there will be nothing to pay)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive down the ramp and exit at Level 2&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive straight to the end of Level 2 and turn right following the exit signs.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; You will see our Off Airport Meet &amp;amp; Greet parking bays opposite the lifts.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Park your car in one of these bays.&amp;nbsp;(PLEASE do not park in Disabled, Brown Badge or Unpaid ticket bays, as Purple Parking will not be held&amp;nbsp;responsible&amp;nbsp;for tickets issued by Heathrow Airport)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Lock your car and give the keys and parking ticket to the Handover Captain, who will be waiting for you&amp;nbsp;at his grey desk&amp;nbsp;near the lift area.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 5 - ARRIVAL INSTRUCTIONS&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;(Postcode for GPS to Terminal 5: TW6 2GA)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow&amp;nbsp;signs for Short stay Passenger pick-up&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive up the ramp,&amp;nbsp;filter to the right and drive under the yellow height restriction arm&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; KEEP&amp;nbsp;to your&amp;nbsp;LEFT&amp;nbsp;and follow the signs&amp;nbsp;for&amp;nbsp;Short stay&amp;nbsp;Level 4.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the Avis signs towards the third set of barriers.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the entrance barrier, take a ticket (there will be nothing to pay).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Once inside, follow the arrows and the&amp;nbsp;P - Off Airport&amp;nbsp;signs to the end of the car park to ROW R &amp;amp; S.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; You will see our Off Airport Meet &amp;amp; Greet parking bays opposite the lifts.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Park in one of these bays&amp;nbsp;(PLEASE do not park in Disabled, Brown Badge or Unpaid ticket bays, as Purple Parking will not be held&amp;nbsp;responsible&amp;nbsp;for tickets issued by Heathrow Airport)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Lock your car and give the keys and parking ticket to the Handover Captain, who will be waiting for you&amp;nbsp;at his grey desk&amp;nbsp;in the lift area near the payment machine.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Our chauffeur will meet you at the terminal at the requested time. Your booking confirmation email will contain precise details.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Full return instructions will be issued by the driver on collection of the vehicle. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0845 850 5859</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; The car park is conveniently located 15-20 minutes away from the Airport.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; The car park offers frequent courtesy bus transfers to the airport which take 15-20 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>&lt;br /&gt;</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>24 hour security guards. CCTV. Purple Parking have been issued with a gold award by the police for security.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&lt;p&gt; Please note that all Heathrow Short Stay Car Parks have height limits.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 1 Short Stay Car Park 1 - 2.05m (6ft 9in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 2 Short Stay Car Park 2 - 2.05m (6ft 9in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 3 Short Stay Car Park 3 - 2.20m (7ft 2in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 4 Short Stay Car Park 4 - 2.00m (6ft 6in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 5 Short Stay Car Park 5 - 2.20m (7ft 2in)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; *Please take this into account if you have a roof luggage box installed on your vehicle*&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; This product is ideal for the disabled traveller.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LHRW.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LHRM</code><airport>LHR</airport><serviceType>O</serviceType><name>PURPLE PARKING BUSINESS PLUS</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Have your car returned to you at the airport by our Handover Captain.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Much better service than any other On-Airport Business car park, at a sensible price.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Drive to car park on departure&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Return meet at airport&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Service is available for all terminals.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; 17 Bath Road, Heathrow, Hounslow, Middlesex, TW6 2AL&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Important Information regarding our Business Parking Plus Service&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; As the company cannot verify what items are left in your vehicle, we would kindly request that you remove any loose items such as&amp;nbsp;Sat Navs, loose cash, sunglasses etc&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; ___________________________________________________________________________&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M25&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Leave the motorway at Junction 15 and follow the M4 signposted to London.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M4&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Leave the motorway at Junction 3 and follow the A312 towards Hounslow / Feltham.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the Jolly Waggoners roundabout turn right onto A4 (Bath Road) towards Heathrow.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Purple Parking Business is approximately 1 mile along the A4 on the left, next door to the Premier Inn Hotel.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>You will be directed to the arrivals area by a Purple Parking Business host.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Your vehicle will be returned to you at the airport terminal.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0845 450 0808</helpline><distanceToAirport>Located 5 minutes from the Airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>The car park offers frequent courtesy bus transfers to the airport which take 5 - 13 minutes.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>5 - 13 Minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park has CCTV, security fencing, 24-hour security guards, spike-strips on entrance and a controlled exit. The car park also has a 'Park Mark' safer parking award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>Height restriction at this car park of 2.15 m (7ft.) which include roof racks and roof boxes.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LHRM.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LHRA</code><airport>LHR</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>PURPLE PARKING LONG STAY</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Excellent service for an economical price!&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;15-20 minute transfer time to airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Pre-book to secure your space and save money.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Height restriction of 2.4m (7ft 4m.)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Security barriers,fencing &amp;amp; lighting &amp;amp; CCTV&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>169 Brent Rd, Southall, Middlesex, UB2 5LE.</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Important Information regarding our Long Stay Service&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; As the company cannot verify what items are left in your vehicle, we would kindly request that you remove any loose items such as&amp;nbsp;Sat Navs, loose cash, sunglasses etc&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; _________________________________________________________________________&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M25&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Leave the motorway at Junction 15 and follow the M4 signposted to London.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M4&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Leave the motorway at Junction 3 and follow the A312 North, signposted to Hayes and Western International Market.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; After 500 yards at the first roundabout, turn right by Tesco in the direction of Southall onto Hayes Road.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the A40(M)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the A312 south, signposted to Hayes after two roundabouts and an underpass.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Turn left at the next roundabout by Tesco in the direction of the Western International Market / Southall onto Hayes Road.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From Hayes Road&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Go past the Western International Market and after about 500 yards, drive straight over the mini roundabout.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; The road bears to the left over a canal bridge.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Brent Road is the next turning on the left at a mini roundabout. (used car lot on that corner)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Purple Parking Long Stay is at the very end of Brent Road after bearing right at the International Trading Estate.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Check in at our arrival kiosk, drive to the car drop off area, hand your car keys to your bus driver and board our courtesy bus.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Please arrive at least 45 minutes before check-in for your flight opens.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Return instructions will be issued on arrival at the car park.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0845 850 5859</helpline><distanceToAirport>The car park is conveniently located 15-20 minutes away from the Airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>The car park offers frequent courtesy bus transfers to and from the airport which take 15-20 minutes.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>15 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations>Cancellations made with at least 24 hrs notice are refunded in full. Within 24 hrs bookings are charged in full.</cancellations><securityMeasures>24 hour security guards. CCTV. Purple Parking have been issued with a gold award by the police for security.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&lt;p&gt; Please note that all Heathrow Short Stay Car Parks have height limits.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 1 Short Stay Car Park 1 - 2.05m (6ft 9in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 2 Short Stay Car Park 2 - 2.05m (6ft 9in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 3 Short Stay Car Park 3 - 2.20m (7ft 2in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 4 Short Stay Car Park 4 - 2.00m (6ft 6in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 5 Short Stay Car Park 5 - 2.20m (7ft 2in)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; *Please take this into account if you have a roof luggage box installed on your vehicle*&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; This product is ideal for the disabled traveller.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LHRA.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LHRC</code><airport>LHR</airport><serviceType>O</serviceType><name>PURPLE PARKING LONG STAY PLUS</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Have your car returned to you at the airport by our Handover Captain.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Park at our economically priced Long Stay Car Park.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Quick and efficient service&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Even better service for not a lot more&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Chauffeur delivers your car on return ONLY.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;You can add a car wash to your booking. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>169 Brent Rd, Southall, Middlesex, UB2 5LE</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Important Information regarding our Long Stay Plus Service&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; As the company cannot verify what items are left in your vehicle, we would kindly request that you remove any loose items such as&amp;nbsp;Sat Navs, loose cash, sunglasses etc&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; ___________________________________________________________________________&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M25&lt;br /&gt; - Leave the motorway at Junction 15 and follow the M4 signposted to London.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M4&lt;br /&gt; - Leave the motorway at Junction 3 and follow the A312 North, signposted to Hayes and Western International Market.&lt;br /&gt; - After 500 yards at the first roundabout, turn right by Tesco in the direction of Southall onto Hayes Road.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the A40(M)&lt;br /&gt; - Follow the A312 south, signposted to Hayes after two roundabouts and an underpass.&lt;br /&gt; - Turn left at the next roundabout by Tesco in the direction of the Western International Market / Southall onto Hayes Road.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From Hayes Road&lt;br /&gt; - Go past the Western International Market and after about 500 yards, drive straight over the mini roundabout.&lt;br /&gt; - The road bears to the left over a canal bridge.&lt;br /&gt; - Brent Road is the next turning on the left at a mini roundabout. (used car lot on that corner)&lt;br /&gt; - Purple Parking Long Stay is at the very end of Brent Road after bearing right at the International Trading Estate.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Check in at our arrival kiosk, drive to the car drop off area, leave your keys in the car and board our courtesy bus.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Please arrive at least 45 minutes before check-in for your flight opens.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Return instructions will be given to you on arrival at the car park.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0845 450 0808</helpline><distanceToAirport>The car park is conviently located 15-20 minutes away from the Airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>The car park offers frequent courtesy bus transfers to the airport which take 15-20 minutes.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>15 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>24 hour security guards. CCTV. Purple Parking have been issued with a gold award by the police for security.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&lt;p&gt; Please note that all Heathrow Short Stay Car Parks have height limits.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 1 Short Stay Car Park 1 - 2.05m (6ft 9in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 2 Short Stay Car Park 2 - 2.05m (6ft 9in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 3 Short Stay Car Park 3 - 2.20m (7ft 2in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 4 Short Stay Car Park 4 - 2.00m (6ft 6in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 5 Short Stay Car Park 5 - 2.20m (7ft 2in)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; *Please take this into account if you have a roof luggage box installed on your vehicle*&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; This product is ideal for the disabled traveller.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LHRC.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LHRB</code><airport>LHR</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>PURPLE PARKING MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Our Handover Captain meets you at the airport and delivers your car back to you on your return.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;The ULTIMATE parking service.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>Quick and Easy access to the terminal.  &lt;br /&gt;Meet and Greet on departure and on your return.  &lt;br /&gt;No transfer required.  &lt;br /&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>169 Brent Road, Southall, Middlesex, UB2 5LE.</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; MEETING POINTS ON ARRIVAL&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The Handover Captains are at their desks from 05.00 every day. (From 04.30 at Terminal 2)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; IF YOU ARE RUNNING EARLY OR LATE, PLEASE CALL THE HELPLINE ON 0845 850 5859&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Important Information regarding our Meet &amp;amp; Greet Service&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; It is essential that you hand over your keys to our representative at the terminal, so that your vehicle can be moved to our car park. Purple Parking can not be held responsible for any car parking costs incurred, if we are not able to move your vehicle.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; As the company cannot verify what items are left in your vehicle, we would kindly request that you remove any loose items such as&amp;nbsp;Sat Navs, loose cash, sunglasses etc.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 1 - ARRIVAL INSTRUCTIONS&amp;nbsp; (Postcode for GPS to Terminal 1: TW6 1AP)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the signs to the Short Stay Car Park 1 (entrance on the ground floor - NOT Short Stay Car Park 1A upstairs)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the entrance barrier, take a ticket (there will be nothing to pay)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Keep to your right and&amp;nbsp;IMMEDIATELY TAKE A FIRST LEFT&amp;nbsp;down to the lower ground floor&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Turn right and drive all the way to the end and bear left after the portacabin (this is not our portacabin), until you are facing the opposite direction&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; You will see our Off Airport Meet &amp;amp; Greet parking bays immediately to your right&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Park your car in one of these bays&amp;nbsp;(PLEASE&amp;nbsp;do not park in Disabled, Brown Badge or Unpaid ticket bays, as Purple Parking will not be&amp;nbsp;responsible&amp;nbsp;for tickets issued by Heathrow Airport)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Lock your car and give the keys and parking ticket to the Handover Captain, who will be waiting for you&amp;nbsp;at his grey desk&amp;nbsp;near the payment machine.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 2 - ARRIVAL INSTRUCTIONS (Postcode for GPS to Terminal 2:&amp;nbsp;TW6 1EW)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Follow signs to the Short Stay Car Park 2&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Drive up the ramp, fork right and drive under the yellow height restriction arm&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Keep&amp;nbsp;to your left and stay in the lane for level 1, 2 &amp;amp; 3 (the car park entrance on your far left) (PLEASE DO NOT ENTER THE CAR PARK ON THE FAR RIGHT HAND BARRIERS)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;At the entrance barrier, take a ticket (there will be nothing to pay)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Drive down the ramp following the P - Off Airport signs and exit at level 2.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Follow the P - Off Airport signs all way round until you reach Rows A and B at the far end of the car park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;You will see our blue Off Airport Meet &amp;amp; Greet parking bays in&amp;nbsp;Row A (Bays 1 to 6) &amp;amp; Row B (Bays 1 - 14)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Park your car in one of these bays&amp;nbsp;(PLEASE&amp;nbsp;do not park in Disabled, Brown Badge or Unpaid ticket bays, as Purple &amp;nbsp;Parking will not be held&amp;nbsp;responsible&amp;nbsp;for tickets issued by Heathrow Airport)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &amp;nbsp;Lock your car and give the keys and parking ticket to the Handover Captain, who will be waiting for you&amp;nbsp;at his grey desk&amp;nbsp;in the lift area near the payment machine.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 3 - ARRIVAL INSTRUCTIONS&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;(Postcode for GPS to Terminal 3: TW6 1QG)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the sign to the Short Stay Car Park 3&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the entrance barrier, take a ticket (there will be nothing to pay)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive up the ramp and exit at level 3&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the road all the way round until you reach Rows A and B at the far end of the Car Park (drive past the first lift area)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; You will see our Off Airport Meet &amp;amp; Greet parking bays opposite the lifts&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Park your car in one of these bays&amp;nbsp;(PLEASE do not park in Disabled, Brown Badge or Unpaid ticket bays, as Purple Parking will not be held&amp;nbsp;responsible&amp;nbsp;for tickets issued by Heathrow Airport)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Lock your car and give the keys and parking ticket to the Handover Captain, who will be waiting for you&amp;nbsp;at his grey desk&amp;nbsp;in the lift area near the payment machine.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 4 - ARRIVAL INSTRUCTIONS&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;(Postcode for GPS to Terminal 4: TW6 3XA)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the signs to short stay car park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive up the ramp and keep to your right&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the entrance barrier, take a ticket (there will be nothing to pay)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive down the ramp and exit at Level 2&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive straight to the end of Level 2 and turn right following the exit signs.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; You will see our Off Airport Meet &amp;amp; Greet parking bays opposite the lifts.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Park your car in one of these bays.&amp;nbsp;(PLEASE do not park in Disabled, Brown Badge or Unpaid ticket bays, as Purple Parking will not be held&amp;nbsp;responsible&amp;nbsp;for tickets issued by Heathrow Airport)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Lock your car and give the keys and parking ticket to the Handover Captain, who will be waiting for you&amp;nbsp;at his grey desk&amp;nbsp;near the lift area.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 5 - ARRIVAL INSTRUCTIONS&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;(Postcode for GPS to Terminal 5: TW6 2GA)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow&amp;nbsp;signs for Short stay Passenger pick-up&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Drive up the ramp,&amp;nbsp;filter to the right and drive under the yellow height restriction arm&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; KEEP&amp;nbsp;to your&amp;nbsp;LEFT&amp;nbsp;and follow the signs&amp;nbsp;for&amp;nbsp;Short stay&amp;nbsp;Level 4.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the Avis signs towards the third set of barriers.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the entrance barrier, take a ticket (there will be nothing to pay).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Once inside, follow the arrows and the&amp;nbsp;P - Off Airport&amp;nbsp;signs to the end of the car park to ROW R &amp;amp; S.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; You will see our Off Airport Meet &amp;amp; Greet parking bays opposite the lifts.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Park in one of these bays&amp;nbsp;(PLEASE do not park in Disabled, Brown Badge or Unpaid ticket bays, as Purple Parking will not be held&amp;nbsp;responsible&amp;nbsp;for tickets issued by Heathrow Airport)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Lock your car and give the keys and parking ticket to the Handover Captain, who will be waiting for you&amp;nbsp;at his grey desk&amp;nbsp;in the lift area near the payment machine.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Our Handover Captain will meet you at the airport at the requested time. Your booking confirmation email will contain precise details.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Full return instructions will be issued by the driver on collection of the vehicle. Please note that if your return flight into Heathrow is delayed beyond midnight, we reserve the right to pick you up at the terminal by courtesy bus and drive you to our car park to collect your vehicle.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0845 850 5859</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; Our chauffeur will meet you at your designated terminal.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport></transferFromAirport><transferTime></transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>24 hour security guards. CCTV. Purple Parking have been issued with a gold award by the police for security.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&lt;p&gt; Please note that all Heathrow Short Stay Car Parks have height limits.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Terminal 1 Short Stay Car Park 1 - 2.05m (6ft 9in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 2 Short Stay Car Park 2 - 2.05m (6ft 9in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 3 Short Stay Car Park 3 - 2.20m (7ft 2in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 4 Short Stay Car Park 4 - 2.00m (6ft 6in)&lt;br /&gt; Terminal 5 Short Stay Car Park 5 - 2.20m (7ft 2in)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; *Please take this into account if you have a roof luggage box installed on your vehicle*&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; This product is ideal for the disabled traveller.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LHRB.jpg</logoURL></carPark></carParks></airport><airport code=\"STN\"><name>London Stansted</name><shortname>londonstansted</shortname><terminals><terminal>1</terminal></terminals><carParks><carPark><code>STNK</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>CSL CAR STORAGE MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Time-saving chauffeur service with off-airport, secure car storage.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Time-saving chauffer service &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Stored on our off-airport car park&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Network House, Takeley Road, Bambers Green, Takeley, Essex CM22 6PF</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; PLEASE CALL 01279 879352 &amp;nbsp;WHEN YOU ARE 20 MINUTES AWAY FROM ARRIVING AT THE AIRPORT. (Failure to do this could result in a delay in CSL getting to you)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Please call CSL on 01279 879 352 &amp;nbsp; - 20 mins before you are due to arrive at the airport to ensure our driver is ready to meet you at the drop-off point which is at the Set Down, outside the Terminal - ZONE C.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; AFTER YOU HAVE COLLECTED YOUR LUGGAGE&amp;nbsp;CALL CSL ON: 01279 879 352&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; MAKE YOUR WAY TO THE PICK UP POINT WHERE YOU DROPPED YOUR VEHICLE OFF, OUTSIDE THE TERMINAL - ZONE C.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The pick up point is clearly signposted inside the terminal and is outside the terminal's main entrance/exit.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; PLEASE DO NOT CALL CSL BEFORE YOU HAVE COLLECTED YOUR LUGGAGE. There is a 15 minute time limit at the pick up point and you will incur additional charges on exit if your vehicle has been at the pick up point any longer than this time period.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>CSL Car Storage is open from 04:00 until Midnight every day with the exception of the Christmas and New Year holidays.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 01279 879352&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>CSL Car Storage is located about 1 mile from the airport terminal.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Your car will be stored in an on-airport car park that has 24 hour guarded security.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>If you have a disability and require assistance please call the office number and requirements will be made for you.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STNK.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STNI</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>CSL CAR STORAGE PARK AND RIDE</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Drop off point located only 1.2 miles from the terminal&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt; transfers every 10-15 minutes to and from the terminal&lt;/li&gt;transfers to the terminal are charged at ?1.00 per person each way.  &lt;br /&gt;Under 16 will be free</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Only 1.2 miles from the terminal&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Transfers run every 10-15 minutes to and from the terminal&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Transfers are charged &amp;pound;1.00 per person each way. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Under 16 will be free &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Network House, Takeley Road, Bambers Green, Takeley, Essex CM22 6PF  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Head to Stansted Airport, On arrival at Stansted airport follow signs for the short stay car park. when you reach Coopers End Roundabout which is the large roundabout before the short stay car park, take the 4th exit signposted 'Takeley'. After taking this exit you will immediately come to a mini roundabout. Turn left at this mini roundabout and head towards Bambers Green. Follow the road for 0.7 miles and you will see 'Network House' on the right hand side. Park your vehicle in the car park at the front of the building and report to reception where you will be checked in and transferred to the airport.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>On arrival at the CSL Drop Off area, Park your car in the area at the front of the building and report to reception. Your details will be checked and you will be required to leave your car keys, your car will be checked and photographed including the mileage and moved to one of our secure parking areas. You will then be transferred to the front of the terminal which is a journey time of 3 minutes.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; AFTER YOU HAVE COLLECTED YOUR LUGGAGE&amp;nbsp;CALL CSL ON: &lt;a&gt;01279 879 352&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; MAKE YOUR WAY TO THE PICK UP POINT WHERE YOU WAS DROPPED OFF, OUTSIDE THE TERMINAL - ZONE C.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The pick up point is clearly signposted inside the terminal and is outside the terminal's main entrance/exit.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; PLEASE DO NOT CALL CSL BEFORE YOU HAVE COLLECTED YOUR LUGGAGE. There is a 15 minute time limit at the pick up point. Therefore CSL will not wait any longer than 15 minutes. You will incur additional charges if CSL have to return to collect you.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>CSL Car Storage is open from 04:00 until Midnight every day with the exception of the Christmas and New Year holidays.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 01279 879352&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>CSL Car Storage is located about 1 mile from the airport terminal.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; CSL Car Storage&amp;nbsp; transfers to and from the airport on demand, which take 3 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>3 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Your car will be stored in an on-airport car park that has 24 hour guarded security.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>If you have a disability and require assistance please call the office number and requirements will be made for you.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STNI.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STNL</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>CSL PREMIUM MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Time-saving chauffeur service with on-airport, secure car parking.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Meet &amp;amp; Service &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Departure &amp;amp; Return &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Stansted Airport, Essex CM24 1RW</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; PLEASE CALL 01279 879352 &amp;nbsp;WHEN YOU ARE 20 MINUTES AWAY FROM ARRIVING AT THE AIRPORT. (Failure to do this could result in a delay in CSL getting to you)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Please call CSL on 01279 879 352 - 20 mins before you are due to arrive at the airport to ensure our driver is ready to meet you at the drop-off point which is at the Set Down, outside the Terminal - ZONE C.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; AFTER YOU HAVE COLLECTED YOUR LUGGAGE&amp;nbsp;CALL CSL ON: 01279 879 352&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; MAKE YOUR WAY TO THE PICK UP POINT WHERE YOU DROPPED YOUR VEHICLE OFF, OUTSIDE THE TERMINAL - ZONE C.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The pick up point is clearly signposted inside the terminal and is outside the terminal's main entrance/exit.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; PLEASE DO NOT CALL CSL BEFORE YOU HAVE COLLECTED YOUR LUGGAGE. There is a 15 minute time limit at the pick up point and you will incur additional charges on exit if your vehicle has been at the pick up point any longer than this time period.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>CSL Car Storage is open from 04:00 until Midnight every day with the exception of the Christmas and New Year holidays.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 01279 879352&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>CSL Car Storage will store your car in an on-airport car park.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Your car will be stored in an on-airport car park that has 24 hour guarded security.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>If you have a disability and require assistance please call the office number and requirements will be made for you.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STNL.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STNO</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>I LOVE MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;The only independent on airport valet parking.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Cars personally collected and delivered on the forecourt outside the terminal doors.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Professional,experienced drivers to meet you personally.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Operated by the UK'S most experienced meet and greet team.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Service available 24 hours per day.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The only independent on airport valet parking&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Cars personally collected and delivered outside terminal&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Professional, experienced drivers&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Meet and greet on departure and return. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Stansted International Airport, Stansted, Essex</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Is it imperative to call prior to arrival, Please call 01279 682230 Option 1 when you are 10 minutes from the airport for your meet location which will be either of the following:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M11: Exit at J8a and follow the A120 directly to the airport.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Orange Short Stay Car Park - Follow signs to the terminal. As you approach the terminal follow signs for short stay car parking and head for the furthest car park, sign posted orange short stay car park’. Take a ticket and follow the road round to the orange bollards, pull in on the left hand side opposite row i, park your car and our driver will meet you there. Please make sure you hand your car park ticket to the driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Express Set Down – Follow signs for terminal as you approach the airport make your way up the ramp sign posted Express set down, look out for two flag poles marked Zone C on right hand side of the set down wait here for your driver to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; (Emergency number only 07972 541638.)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From Colchester: Take the A120 towards Bishop’s Stortford and follow the signs for the airport.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Orange Short Stay Car Park - Follow signs to the terminal. As you approach the terminal follow signs for short stay car parking and head for the furthest car park, sign posted orange short stay car park’. Take a ticket and follow the road round to the orange bollards, pull in on the left hand side opposite row i, park your car and our driver will meet you there. Please make sure you hand your car park ticket to the driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Express Set Down – Follow signs for terminal as you approach the airport make your way up the ramp sign posted Express set down, look out for two flag poles marked Zone C on right hand side of the set down wait here for your driver to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; (Emergency number only 07972 541638.)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Please call 01279 682230 Option 1 when you are 10 minutes from the airport. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Express Set Down – Follow signs for Express Set Down which is located directly outside the terminal building up on the forecourt. Drive along to the area marked zone C located centrally on right hand side of the terminal road.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If there are issues with the forecourt you may be told&amp;nbsp; when you call to go to the Orange Short Stay Car Park instead (do not go here unless you are told to)- Follow signs to the terminal. As you approach the terminal follow signs for short stay car parking and head for the furthest car park, sign posted orange short stay car park’. Take a ticket and follow the road round to the orange bollards, pull in on the left hand side, park and your driver will meet you there. Please make sure you hand your car park ticket to the driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If you experience difficulties with our main contact number please use the Emergency number 07972 541638 to contact the drivers.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Please collect all your luggage and clear customs before calling 01279 682230 Option 1 to have your car delivered. Make your way to the forecourt, just outside the terminal doors and wait in Zone C by the flag poles. Please remain on the same level as departures. We are unable to wait for more than 5 minutes so it is therefore essential you are ready to collect your car otherwise you may be liable for any excess fees&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; On occasions the airport will make operational changes to the forecourt. You will be informed if this is the case when you call and our alternative return point is the Orange Short Stay Car park &amp;nbsp;- When exiting the terminal turn left toward stairs go down one level to Orange Short Stay Car park, This car park has a 10 minute free period. It is therefore essential you are ready to collect your car otherwise you will be liable for any excess car park fees&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If you experience difficulties with our main contact number please use the Emergency number 07972 541638 to contact the drivers.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Purple Parking &amp;nbsp;Meet &amp;amp; Greet is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>07972 541638</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park has 24 hour security and has barrier entry, lighting and CCTV.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STNO.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STN8</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>I LOVE PARK AND RIDE</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Independent On-Airport car park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Free Shuttle buses on demand.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Pick up and drop off on forecourt outside terminal doors.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Terminal only 1.5 miles away.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;p&gt;&amp;middot;&amp;nbsp; Independent On-Airport car park. &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;middot;&amp;nbsp; Free Shuttle buses on demand. &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;middot;&amp;nbsp; Pick up and drop off&amp;nbsp; outside terminal doors. &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;middot;&amp;nbsp; Terminal only 1.5 miles away.&lt;/p&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Southgate, Stansted Airport, CM24 1PY&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Follow signs from the motorway towards the mid-stay car park, using post code CM24 1PY in your Sat Nav. Our car park is located next to Holiday Inn, just opposite MacDonald’s and before the BP garage. Turn in to the Holiday Inn entrance and then immediately on the right hand side is the entrance to our car park.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Please park in a customer parking space on the right hand side. Go to Reception to check- in, before unloading your bags to check in. Please load your bags in to our transfer bus.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Please ensure you collect all your luggage and clear customs before calling 01279 682233 (option1) to be collected. Make your way to the forecourt, just outside the terminal doors and wait in Zone C by the flag poles. Please remain on the same level as departures. We are unable to wait for more than 5 minutes so it is therefore essential you are ready to be collected otherwise you may be liable for any excess fees we incur. Emergency number – 07972 541638&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Purple Parking &amp;nbsp;Meet &amp;amp; Greet is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 01279 682233 (option 1)&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; I Love Park and Ride&amp;nbsp; is located about 1.5 mile from the airport terminal.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;Transfers to and from the airport on demand, which take 5 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>5 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park has 24 hour security and has barrier entry, lighting and CCTV.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STN8.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STN2</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>JETPARKS</name><description>Jetparks is our best value, no frills car park.  &lt;br /&gt;Free shuttle buses run every 20 minutes.  &lt;br /&gt;Ideal for family holidays on a budget.  &lt;br /&gt;Official On Airport car park.</description><furtherInformation></furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Jetparks , Round Coppice Road, Stansted Airport, Essex, CM24 1RY&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Directions from London&amp;nbsp;- Please exit the M11 at Junction 8a and follow the below directions&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the left hand lane and follow the filter left. Go straight ahead at the next roundabout, passing the Hilton hotel on your left. At the next roundabout go straight on passing the entrance to the official Long Stay Car park. At the next roundabout follow signs LEFT for entrance to Jetparks.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Directions from Cambridge.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the first exit at the roundabout. At the next roundabout take the second exit, signposted Long Stay car park. At the next roundabout go straight on passing the entrance to the official Long Stay Car park. At the next roundabout follow signs LEFT for entrance to Jetparks.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &amp;nbsp;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Entry Procedure:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Your registration number will be recognised at the entry barrier and a ticket will be printed showing your registration and booking ref. &amp;nbsp;If a ticket is not issued automatically, please press intercom button for assistance. &amp;nbsp;Do NOT insert Credit Card.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Exit Procedure:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Drive up to the exit barrier. Insert the ticket that was issued on entry to the car park. &amp;nbsp;If you have pre-booked DO NOT insert Credit Card at the barrier as you may be charged again. &amp;nbsp;The barrier will open and you may proceed out of the exit.&amp;nbsp; If you experience any difficulties, please press the call button for assistance.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; This car park is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0871 310 4111&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; 10-12 Minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfer from car park to terminal:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The courtesy bus takes 10 - 12 minutes to the terminal.&amp;nbsp; Buses arrive every&amp;nbsp;20 minutes and are available from 04:00 to 22:00. During the period of 22:00 and 04:00 please press the call button for assistance and the Long Stay bus will arrive to the bus stop.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Transfer from terminal to car park:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; On arrival for a period from 04:00 to 22:00 follow signs for &amp;quot;Buses to&amp;nbsp;JetParks car park&amp;quot;, for a period from 22:00 to 04:00 follow signs for &amp;quot;Buses to Long Stay car park&amp;quot; and inform a bus driver that you are going to JetParks car park. Courtesy coaches are located at the&amp;nbsp;JetParks (or Long Stay) bus stops in front of the terminal. Please ensure that the coach you board is going to the correct zone indicated on your ticket.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Car park is manned 24hrs, frequently patrolled and enclosed by security fencing. Comprehensive CCTV in operation.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; This car park is a recipient of the Park Mark, Safer Parking Award from the British Parking Association.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STN2.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STN1</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>LONG STAY</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Long Stay offers On Airport Parking at Off-site prices.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Free shuttle buses run every 15 minutes.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Just a short 8 - 10 minute journey to the Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt; Ideal for 1 - 2 week stays.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Long Stay, Round Coppice Road, Stansted Airport, Essex, CM24 1SE&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Directions from London&amp;nbsp;- Please exit the M11 at Junction 8a and follow the below directions&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the left hand lane and follow the filter left. &amp;nbsp;At Priory Wood Roundabout take the 1st exit onto Round Coppice Road, you will pass the Hilton hotel on your left and at the next roundabout take the first exit into the Long Stay car park.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Directions from Cambridge&amp;nbsp;- Please exit the M11 at Junction 8 and follow the below directions&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the A120 exit to Stansted Airport. &amp;nbsp;At Priory Wood Roundabout take the 2nd exit onto Round Coppice Road. &amp;nbsp;At the next roundabout take the first exit, you will pass the Hilton hotel on your left and at the next roundabout take the first exit into the Long Stay car park.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Entry Procedure: Your registration number will be recognised at the entry barrier and a ticket will be printed showing your registration and booking ref. &amp;nbsp;If a ticket is not issued automatically, please press intercom button for assistance. &amp;nbsp;Do NOT insert Credit Card</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Exit Procedure:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Drive up to the exit barrier. Insert the ticket that was issued on entry to the car park. &amp;nbsp;If you have pre-booked DO NOT insert Credit Card at the barrier as you may be charged again. &amp;nbsp;The barrier will open and you may proceed out of the exit.&amp;nbsp; If you experience any difficulties, please press the call button for assistance.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; This car park is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0871 310 4111&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; 8-10 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfer from car park to terminal:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the 8-10 minute courtesy bus shuttle to the terminal.&amp;nbsp; Buses arrive every 15 minutes and are available 24 hours per day.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Transfer from terminal to car park:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; On arrival follow signs for &a