 Junction 8 and follow the below directions&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the A120 exit to Stansted Airport. &amp;nbsp;At Priory Wood Roundabout take the 2nd exit onto Round Coppice Road. &amp;nbsp;At the next roundabout take the first exit, you will pass the Hilton hotel on your left and at the next roundabout take the first exit into the Long Stay Saver car park.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Entry Procedure:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Your registration number will be recognised at the entry barrier and a ticket will be printed showing your registration and booking ref. &amp;nbsp;If a ticket is not issued automatically, please press intercom button for assistance. &amp;nbsp;Do NOT insert Credit Card&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Exit Procedure:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Drive up to the exit barrier. Insert the ticket that was issued on entry to the car park. &amp;nbsp;If you have pre-booked DO NOT insert Credit Card at the barrier as you may be charged again. &amp;nbsp;The barrier will open and you may proceed out of the exit.&amp;nbsp; If you experience any difficulties, please press the call button for assistance.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; This car park is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0871 310 4111&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; 8 - 10 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfer from car park to terminal:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the 8-10 minute courtesy bus shuttle to the terminal.&amp;nbsp; Buses arrive every 15 minutes and are available 24 hours per day.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Transfer from terminal to car park:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; On arrival follow signs for &amp;quot;Buses to Long Stay car park&amp;quot;. Courtesy coaches are located at the Long Stay bus stops in front of the terminal. Please ensure that the coach you board is going to the correct zone indicated on your ticket.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>8 - 10 Minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Car park is manned 24hrs, frequently patrolled and enclosed by security fencing. Comprehensive CCTV in operation.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; This car park is a recipient of the Park Mark, Safer Parking Award from the British Parking Association.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STN6.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STN9</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>MAPLE MANOR MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;New product!!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Over 21 years Meet &amp;amp; Greet experience&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Hassle-free chauffeur service - your vehicle is collected and returned to you at the airport.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation></furtherInformation><address>Stansted International Airport, Stansted, Essex</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Please call Maple Manor when you are 10 minutes away from Stansted Airport&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Leave the M11 by the slip road at Junction 8 Southbound or Junction 8a North Bound&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the end of the road follow it round to the left onto A120 Thremhall Avenue&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; You’ll come to a large roundabout – take the 3rd exit onto A120 Thremhall Avenue&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Continue down this road and keep left towards the Bassingbourn Roundabout and take the 2nd Exit onto Thremhall avenue&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the next roundabout Coopers end roundabout take the 2nd exit onto Terminal Road North.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow signs for “the Set Down Area Zone C” where you will be met by your driver - park as close as you can to the two flags poles.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Please call 01279 210590 ten minutes before arriving at the airport.&amp;nbsp;You will need to head towards the Express set down in Zone C. This is located in front of the airport terminal.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Please drive to the barriers at departure level at the terminal where the Automatic Number Plate Recognition will let you through. If you need any assistance please use the intercom and make sure you have your confirmation and reference ready.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; *Meeting point is subject to change on the day by Stansted Airport – you will be informed if this is the case when you call.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Once you have collected all of your luggage, please call 01279 210590 to arrange collection of your vehicle.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; Your car will be returned to the Express set down in Zone C which is usually where you dropped it off. This is located in front of the airport terminal.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; *Meeting point is subject to change on the day by Stansted Airport – you will be informed if this is the case when you call.&lt;br /&gt; This will be located at the front of the airport terminal.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods></openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 01279 210590&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures></securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STN9.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STN7</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>MEET AND GREET SAVER</name><description>&lt;li&gt;The only official Stansted Meet &amp;amp; Greet Service.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Check In just a short stroll away.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Fully insured Meet &amp;amp; Greet operator.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt; Bookings for this service cannot be amended or cancelled.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Extra saving - non flexible booking. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Ideal if you’ve got heavy luggage, are traveling with children or just want a hassle-free route to check-in&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Your vehicle will remain in secure storage&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Flight check–in is only a short walk away&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Your vehicle will be waiting for you upon your return&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Suitable for both business and leisure travel&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt;Meet &amp;amp; Greet Saver, Stansted Airport, Essex, CM24 1RW&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Directions from London&amp;nbsp;- Please exit the M11 at Junction 8a and follow the below directions&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Follow the road for just over 1 mile and take the Stansted Airport exit and branch left.&amp;nbsp; At Bassingbourn roundabout take the 2nd exit onto Thremhall Avenue.&amp;nbsp; At Coopers End Roundabout take the third exit following signs to the Short Stay Car Parks.&amp;nbsp; Take the second entrance on the left signposted&amp;nbsp;M&amp;amp;G.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Directions from Cambridge&amp;nbsp;- Please exit the M11 at Junction 8 and follow the below directions&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the A120 exit to Stansted Airport.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; At Priory Wood Roundabout take the 3rd exit, merge onto the A120 and branch left.&amp;nbsp; At Bassingbourn roundabout take the 2nd exit onto Thremhall Avenue.&amp;nbsp; At Coopers End Roundabout take the third exit following signs to the Short Stay Car Parks. Take the second entrance on the left signposted&amp;nbsp;M&amp;amp;G.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Drive to the Meet &amp;amp; Greet Car Park signposted as&amp;nbsp;M&amp;amp;G.&amp;nbsp;Approach the Barrier and your vehicle will activate a call to the customer services staff who will provide parking instructions and raise the barrier. Once parked in the relevant lane secure your vehicle and take your keys to the Meet &amp;amp; Greet Reception Office.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On return from your trip please go to the Meet &amp;amp; Greet Reception office located by the Meet&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp; Greet Saver car park. Staff will return your keys and direct you to your car.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Hours of operation: 24 hours. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 01279 680095&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; You will be met at the Airport Terminal.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport></transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Your car will be parked in a secure and official on-airport car park whilst you're away.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; Blue Badge holders - Please contact us directly once booked so that we can try to cater for individual requirements&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STN7.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STNH</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>METEOR MEET AND GREET PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;The only independent on airport valet parking.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Cars personally collected and delivered on the forecourt outside the terminal doors.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Professional,experienced drivers to meet you personally.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Operated by the UK'S most experienced meet and greet team.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Service available 24 hours per day.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The only independent on airport valet parking.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;You car collected and delivered outside the terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Professional, experienced drivers meet and greet you.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Service available 24 hours per day &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Stansted International Airport, Stansted, Essex</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Is it imperative to call prior to arrival, Please call 01279 682230 Option 1 when you are 10 minutes from the airport for your meet location which will be either of the following:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M11: Exit at J8a and follow the A120 directly to the airport.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Orange Short Stay Car Park - Follow signs to the terminal. As you approach the terminal follow signs for short stay car parking and head for the furthest car park, sign posted orange short stay car park’. Take a ticket and follow the road round to the orange bollards, pull in on the left hand side opposite row i, park your car and our driver will meet you there. Please make sure you hand your car park ticket to the driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Express Set Down – Follow signs for terminal as you approach the airport make your way up the ramp sign posted Express set down, look out for two flag poles marked Zone C on right hand side of the set down wait here for your driver to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; (Emergency number only 07972 541638.)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From Colchester: Take the A120 towards Bishop’s Stortford and follow the signs for the airport.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Orange Short Stay Car Park - Follow signs to the terminal. As you approach the terminal follow signs for short stay car parking and head for the furthest car park, sign posted orange short stay car park’. Take a ticket and follow the road round to the orange bollards, pull in on the left hand side opposite row i, park your car and our driver will meet you there. Please make sure you hand your car park ticket to the driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Express Set Down – Follow signs for terminal as you approach the airport make your way up the ramp sign posted Express set down, look out for two flag poles marked Zone C on right hand side of the set down wait here for your driver to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; (Emergency number only 07972 541638.)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Please call 01279 682230 Option 1 when you are 10 minutes from the airport. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Express Set Down – Follow signs for Express Set Down which is located directly outside the terminal building up on the forecourt. Drive along to the area marked zone C located centrally on right hand side of the terminal road.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If there are issues with the forecourt you may be told&amp;nbsp; when you call to go to the Orange Short Stay Car Park instead (do not go here unless you are told to)- Follow signs to the terminal. As you approach the terminal follow signs for short stay car parking and head for the furthest car park, sign posted orange short stay car park’. Take a ticket and follow the road round to the orange bollards, pull in on the left hand side, park and your driver will meet you there. Please make sure you hand your car park ticket to the driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If you experience difficulties with our main contact number please use the Emergency number 07972 541638 to contact the drivers.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Please collect all your luggage and clear customs before calling 01279 682230 Option 1 to have your car delivered. Make your way to the forecourt, just outside the terminal doors and wait in Zone C by the flag poles. Please remain on the same level as departures. We are unable to wait for more than 5 minutes so it is therefore essential you are ready to collect your car otherwise you may be liable for any excess fees&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; On occasions the airport will make operational changes to the forecourt. You will be informed if this is the case when you call and our alternative return point is the Orange Short Stay Car park &amp;nbsp;- When exiting the terminal turn left toward stairs go down one level to Orange Short Stay Car park, This car park has a 10 minute free period. It is therefore essential you are ready to collect your car otherwise you will be liable for any excess car park fees&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If you experience difficulties with our main contact number please use the Emergency number 07972 541638 to contact the drivers.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Non-Flex&amp;nbsp; Meet &amp;amp; Greet is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>07972 541638</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; The car park has 24 hour security and has barrier entry, lighting and CCTV.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>12</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; If you have a disability and require assistance please call the office number and requirements will be made for you.&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STNH.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STN3</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>OFFICIAL MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;The only official Stansted Meet and Greet Service.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Check In just a short stroll away.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Fully insured Meet &amp;amp; Greet operator.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt; Ideal for any duration.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;A Official Stansted Meet &amp;amp; Greet Service.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Check is just a short stroll away.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Fully insured Meet and Greet operator.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Ideal for any duration.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Meet &amp;amp; Greet, Stansted Airport, Essex, CM24 1RW&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Directions from London&amp;nbsp;- Please exit the M11 at Junction 8a and follow the below directions&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Follow the road for just over 1 mile and take the Stansted Airport exit and branch left.&amp;nbsp; At Bassingbourn roundabout take the 2nd exit onto Thremhall Avenue.&amp;nbsp; At Coopers End Roundabout take the third exit following signs to the Short Stay Car Parks.&amp;nbsp; Take the second entrance on the left signposted&amp;nbsp;M&amp;amp;G.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Directions from Cambridge&amp;nbsp;- Please exit the M11 at Junction 8 and follow the below directions&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the A120 exit to Stansted Airport.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; At Priory Wood Roundabout take the 3rd exit, merge onto the A120 and branch left.&amp;nbsp; At Bassingbourn roundabout take the 2nd exit onto Thremhall Avenue.&amp;nbsp; At Coopers End Roundabout take the third exit following signs to the Short Stay Car Parks. Take the second entrance on the left signposted&amp;nbsp;M&amp;amp;G.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Drive to the Meet &amp;amp; Greet Car Park signposted as&amp;nbsp;M&amp;amp;G.&amp;nbsp;Approach the Barrier and your vehicle will activate a call to the customer services staff who will provide parking instructions and raise the barrier. Once parked in the relevant lane secure your vehicle and take your keys to the Meet &amp;amp; Greet Reception Office.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On return from your trip please go to the Meet &amp;amp; Greet Reception office located by the Meet&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp; Greet&amp;nbsp;car park. Staff will return your keys and direct you to your car.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Hours of operation: 24 hours. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 01279 680095&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; You will be met at the Airport Terminal.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport></transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Your car will be parked in a secure and official on-airport car park whilst you're away.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; Blue Badge holders - Please contact us directly once booked so that we can try to cater for individual requirements&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STN3.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STN12</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>OFFICIAL MEET AND GREET 10% OFF SAVER</name><description>&lt;li&gt;The only official Stansted Meet and Greet Service.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Check In just a short stroll away.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Fully insured Meet &amp;amp; Greet operator.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt; Ideal for any duration.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;BOOKINGS CAN NOT BE AMENDED OR REFUNDED WITH THIS PARKING SERVICE&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;A Official Stansted Meet &amp;amp; Greet Service.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Check is just a short stroll away.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Fully insured Meet and Greet operator.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Ideal for any duration.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Meet &amp;amp; Greet, Stansted Airport, Essex, CM24 1RW</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Directions from London&amp;nbsp;- Please exit the M11 at Junction 8a and follow the below directions&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Follow the road for just over 1 mile and take the Stansted Airport exit and branch left.&amp;nbsp; At Bassingbourn roundabout take the 2nd exit onto Thremhall Avenue.&amp;nbsp; At Coopers End Roundabout take the third exit following signs to the Short Stay Car Parks.&amp;nbsp; Take the second entrance on the left signposted&amp;nbsp;M&amp;amp;G.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Directions from Cambridge&amp;nbsp;- Please exit the M11 at Junction 8 and follow the below directions&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the A120 exit to Stansted Airport.&amp;nbsp; At Priory Wood Roundabout take the 3rd exit, merge onto the A120 and branch left.&amp;nbsp; At Bassingbourn roundabout take the 2nd exit onto Thremhall Avenue.&amp;nbsp; At Coopers End Roundabout take the third exit following signs to the Short Stay Car Parks. Take the second entrance on the left signposted&amp;nbsp;M&amp;amp;G.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Drive to the Meet &amp;amp; Greet Car Park signposted as&amp;nbsp;M&amp;amp;G.&amp;nbsp;Approach the Barrier and your vehicle will activate a call to the customer services staff who will provide parking instructions and raise the barrier. Once parked in the relevant lane secure your vehicle and take your keys to the Meet &amp;amp; Greet Reception Office.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>On return from your trip please go to the Meet &amp;amp; Greet Reception office located by the Meet&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp; Greet&amp;nbsp;car park. Staff will return your keys and direct you to your car.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Hours of operation: 24 hours. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>01279 680095  &lt;br /&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>You will be met at the Airport Terminal.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport></transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Your car will be parked in a secure and official on-airport car park whilst you're away.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; Blue Badge holders - Please contact us directly once booked so that we can try to cater for individual requirements&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STN12.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STNM</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>PINK ELEPHANT PARK AND RIDE</name><description>&lt;li&gt;The car park is located just 1.2 miles away from the Terminal Building.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Transfers take approximately 5 minutes.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Only 1.2 miles away from the terminal. &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Pre-book to secure your space and save money.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;&amp;pound;1.00 each way per adult.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;16 years of age are free&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Pink Elephant&amp;nbsp; - Network House, Takeley Road, Bambers Green, Takeley, Essex, CM22 6PF.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Head towards Stansted Airport Terminal.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; At the roundabout just before the Terminal (A), take the 4th exit signposted 'Takeley'.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; At the next mini roundabout, take the first exit (Takeley Road). CSL is approximately 3/4 mile along Takeley Road, on the right hand side.&lt;br /&gt; For SatNav purposes the office address is, CSL,Network House, Takeley Road, Bambers Green, Takeley, Essex, CM22 6PF, Tel: 01279 879352.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On arrival at the CSL Drop Off area, Park your car in the area at the front of the building and report to reception. Your details will be checked and you will be required to leave your car keys, your car will be checked and photographed including the mileage and moved to one of our secure parking areas. You will then be transferred to the front of the terminal which is a journey time of 3 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; After clearing customs, call 01279 879352 to advise you have returned, then proceed to Zone C, by the flags, where you were dropped off on outbound journey.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; -&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; The transfer bus operates between 0400-0000.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; -&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Transfers to/from the terminal are GBP/&amp;pound;1.00 each way per adult.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; -&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Children under 16 years of age are free.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Non-Flex&amp;nbsp; Meet &amp;amp; Greet is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 01279 879 352&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; CSL Car Storage is located about 1 mile from the airport terminal.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; CSL Car Storage&amp;nbsp; transfers to and from the airport on demand, which take 3 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>8 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; The car park has 24 hour security and has barrier entry, lighting and CCTV.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; If you have a disability and require assistance please call the office number and requirements will be made for you.&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STNM.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STN5</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>PURPLE PARKING</name><description>A Brand New car park which is our cloest to the terminal self-park option, allowing you qick access to check-in for a hasle-free start to your trip.  &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Purple Parking , Round Coppice Road, Stansted Airport, Essex, CM24 1RY.&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Directions from London&amp;nbsp;- Please exit the M11 at Junction 8a and follow the below directions&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the left hand lane and follow the filter left. Go straight ahead at the next roundabout, passing the Hilton hotel on your left. At the next roundabout go straight on passing the entrance to the official Long Stay Car park. At the next roundabout follow signs LEFT for entrance to Purple Parking.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Directions from Cambridge&lt;/p&gt; &amp;nbsp;  &lt;p&gt; Take the first exit at the roundabout. At the next roundabout take the second exit, signposted Long Stay car park. At the next roundabout go straight on passing the entrance to the official Long Stay Car park. At the next roundabout follow signs LEFT for entrance to Purple Parking.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Entry Procedure:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Your registration number will be recognised at the entry barrier and a ticket will be printed showing your registration and booking ref. &amp;nbsp;If a ticket is not issued automatically, please press intercom button for assistance. &amp;nbsp;Do NOT insert Credit Card.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Exit Procedure:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Drive up to the exit barrier. Insert the ticket that was issued on entry to the car park. &amp;nbsp;If you have pre-booked DO NOT insert Credit Card at the barrier as you may be charged again. &amp;nbsp;The barrier will open and you may proceed out of the exit.&amp;nbsp; If you experience any difficulties, please press the call button for assistance.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; This car park is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0871 310 4111&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; 10-12 Minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfer from car park to terminal:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The courtesy bus takes 10 - 12 minutes to the terminal. &amp;nbsp;Buses arrive every&amp;nbsp;20 minutes and are available from 04:00 to 22:00. During the period of 22:00 and 04:00 please press the call button for assistance and the Long Stay bus will arrive to the bus stop.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Transfer from terminal to car park:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; On arrival for a period from 04:00 to 22:00 follow signs for &amp;quot;Buses to&amp;nbsp;JetParks car park&amp;quot;, for a period from 22:00 to 04:00 follow signs for &amp;quot;Buses to Long Stay car park&amp;quot; and inform a bus driver that you are going to JetParks car park. Courtesy coaches are located at the&amp;nbsp;JetParks (or Long Stay) bus stops in front of the terminal. Please ensure that the coach you board is going to the correct zone indicated on your ticket.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>10-12 Minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Car park is manned 24hrs, frequently patrolled and enclosed by security fencing. Comprehensive CCTV in operation.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; This car park is a recipient of the Park Mark, Safer Parking Award from the British Parking Association.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STN5.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STNQ</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>PURPLE PARKING MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Genuine Valet parking by the UK''s most experienced team.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Your car will always be collected and returned by a driver on the forecourt outside the terminal doors.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;No hidden costs.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Secure, Park Mark accredited car parks.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;You will be collected and returned by our Chauffeur outside the terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Secure&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Park Mark accredited car parks.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Stansted International Airport, Stansted, Essex</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Is it imperative to call prior to arrival, Please call 01279 682230 Option 1 when you are 10 minutes from the airport for your meet location which will be either of the following:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M11: Exit at J8a and follow the A120 directly to the airport.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Orange Short Stay Car Park - Follow signs to the terminal. As you approach the terminal follow signs for short stay car parking and head for the furthest car park, sign posted orange short stay car park’. Take a ticket and follow the road round to the orange bollards, pull in on the left hand side opposite row i, park your car and our driver will meet you there. Please make sure you hand your car park ticket to the driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Express Set Down – Follow signs for terminal as you approach the airport make your way up the ramp sign posted Express set down, look out for two flag poles marked Zone C on right hand side of the set down wait here for your driver to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; (Emergency number only 07972 541638.)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From Colchester: Take the A120 towards Bishop’s Stortford and follow the signs for the airport.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Orange Short Stay Car Park - Follow signs to the terminal. As you approach the terminal follow signs for short stay car parking and head for the furthest car park, sign posted orange short stay car park’. Take a ticket and follow the road round to the orange bollards, pull in on the left hand side opposite row i, park your car and our driver will meet you there. Please make sure you hand your car park ticket to the driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Express Set Down – Follow signs for terminal as you approach the airport make your way up the ramp sign posted Express set down, look out for two flag poles marked Zone C on right hand side of the set down wait here for your driver to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; (Emergency number only 07972 541638.)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Please call 01279 682230 Option 1 when you are 10 minutes from the airport. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Express Set Down – Follow signs for Express Set Down which is located directly outside the terminal building up on the forecourt. Drive along to the area marked zone C located centrally on right hand side of the terminal road.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If there are issues with the forecourt you may be told&amp;nbsp; when you call to go to the Orange Short Stay Car Park instead (do not go here unless you are told to)- Follow signs to the terminal. As you approach the terminal follow signs for short stay car parking and head for the furthest car park, sign posted orange short stay car park’. Take a ticket and follow the road round to the orange bollards, pull in on the left hand side, park and your driver will meet you there. Please make sure you hand your car park ticket to the driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If you experience difficulties with our main contact number please use the Emergency number 07972 541638 to contact the drivers.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Please collect all your luggage and clear customs before calling 01279 682230 Option 1 to have your car delivered. Make your way to the forecourt, just outside the terminal doors and wait in Zone C by the flag poles. Please remain on the same level as departures. We are unable to wait for more than 5 minutes so it is therefore essential you are ready to collect your car otherwise you may be liable for any excess fees&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; On occasions the airport will make operational changes to the forecourt. You will be informed if this is the case when you call and our alternative return point is the Orange Short Stay Car park &amp;nbsp;- When exiting the terminal turn left toward stairs go down one level to Orange Short Stay Car park, This car park has a 10 minute free period. It is therefore essential you are ready to collect your car otherwise you will be liable for any excess car park fees&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If you experience difficulties with our main contact number please use the Emergency number 07972 541638 to contact the drivers.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Purple Parking &amp;nbsp;Meet &amp;amp; Greet is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>07972 541638</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park has 24 hour security and has barrier entry, lighting and CCTV.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STNQ.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STNP</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>STANSTED OFF SITE PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Off-airport, secure car parking near Stansted Airport.&lt;/li&gt; transfers every 10-15 minutes to and from the terminal.transfers to the terminal are charged at &amp;pound;1.00 per person each way.</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Off Airport parking&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Secure car park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Transfers every 10-15 minutes.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Park &amp;amp; Ride. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Transfer charge is &amp;pound;1.00 per person each way&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>The Old Corn Barn, Pledgdon Hall, Henham, Stansted, CM22 6BJ.</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Please call 07909 546847 fifteen minutes prior to your arrival so that our bus driver can meet you at the parking facility.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; DIRECTIONS FROM THE M11 AND A120.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; FOLLOW THE SIGNS FOR STANSTED AIRPORT.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; FOLLOW THE SIGNS FOR THE TERMINAL.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; WHEN YOU COME TO COOPERS END ROUNDABOUT TAKE THE 4TH EXIT SIGNPOSTED TAKLEY.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; YOU WILL IMEDIATLEY COME TO A SMALL MINI ROUNDABOUT TURN LEFT.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; CONTINUE ON THIS ROAD YOU WILL COME TO ANOTHER ROUNDABOUT GO STRAIGHT OVER.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; AFTER APROXIMATLEY 1 MILE YOU WILL COME TO A T JUNCTION THE CROWN PUB WILL BE IN FRONT OF YOU.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; TURN RIGHT ON TO HENHAM ROAD.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; CONTINUE FOR 1.1 MILES OUR CAR PARK IS ON YOUR RIGHT HAND SIDE WE SHARE OUR PREMISES WITH PRACTICAL CAR AND VAN RENTAL.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; PARK ON THE RIGHTHAND SIDE IF POSSIBLE, MAKE A NOTE OF YOUR MILAGE, RECEPTION IS AT THE TOP OF THE BUILDING.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Please call 07909 546847 fifteen minutes prior to your arrival so that our bus driver can meet you at the parking facility.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>On your return please call 07909 546847 to arrange for the bus to collect you.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Stansted Off Site Parking is open from 04:00 until Midnight every day.</openingPeriods><helpline>01279 850379</helpline><distanceToAirport>Stansted Off Site Parking's secure car park is located less than 5 miles from the airport terminal.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers operate on demand to and from the airport and take about 10 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>10 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park has CCTV and holds the 'Park Mark' safer parking award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STNP.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>STN4</code><airport>STN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>VALET PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Arrive at the Airport in style.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Exclusive access to the Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Your car will be returned to the Premium Collection zone.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt; FREE FastTrack through security for all of your travelling party.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;p&gt;&amp;middot;&amp;nbsp; Arrive at the Airport in style.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;middot;&amp;nbsp; Exclusive access to the Terminal.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;middot;&amp;nbsp; Your car will be returned to the Premium Collection zone.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;middot;&amp;nbsp; FREE FastTrack through security for all parties traveling.&amp;nbsp; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Valet Parking, Stansted Airport, Essex, CM24 1RW.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Directions from London&amp;nbsp;- Please exit the M11 at Junction 8a and follow the below directions&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Follow the road for just over 1 mile and take the Stansted Airport exit and branch left.&amp;nbsp; At Bassingbourn roundabout take the 2nd exit onto Thremhall Avenue.&amp;nbsp;At Coopers End Roundabout take the 2nd exit towards the Terminal Forecourt signposted as Express Set Down &amp;amp; Airport Valet in zone D. The Valet Drop Off points are located in zone D at the far end of the forecourt.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Directions from Cambridge&amp;nbsp;- Please exit the M11 at Junction 8 and follow the below directions&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the A120 exit to Stansted Airport.&amp;nbsp; At Priory Wood Roundabout take the 3rd exit, merge onto the A120 and branch left.&amp;nbsp; Take the 2nd&amp;nbsp;exit off Bassingbourn roundabout onto Thremhall Avenue.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; At Coopers End Roundabout take the 2nd exit towards the Terminal Forecourt signposted as Express Set Down &amp;amp; Airport Valet in zone D. The Valet Drop Off points are located in zone D at the far end of the forecourt.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The Valet staff will complete a form with you and park your vehicle for you on-airport, in one of our secure car parks.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; At Coopers End Roundabout take the 2nd exit towards the Terminal Forecourt signposted as Express Set Down &amp;amp; Airport Valet in zone D. Please drive to zone D at the far end of the terminal forecourt to the valet parking drop-off point. The valet staff will complete a form with you and park your vehicle for you on-airport in one of our secure car parks.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On return from you trip please go to the Meet &amp;amp; Greet Reception Office located by the Meet &amp;amp; Greet car park. &amp;nbsp;Valet Staff will return your keys and escort you to your vehicle advising you of the exit procedure.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Hours of operation: 24 hours. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 01279 680095&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; You will be met at the Airport Terminal.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport></transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Your car will be parked in a secure and official on-airport car park whilst you're away.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>&lt;p&gt; Blue Badge holders - Please contact us directly once booked so that we can try to cater for individual requirements&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/STN4.jpg</logoURL></carPark></carParks></airport><airport code=\"LTN\"><name>Luton Airport</name><shortname>lutonairport</shortname><terminals><terminal>1</terminal></terminals><carParks><carPark><code>LTNU</code><airport>LTN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>AIRPARKS DROP &amp; GO SUPERSAVER</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Money-Saving off-airport secure parking.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Extra savings for non-flexible bookings.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Extra savings - Non flexible booking.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;All buses have disabled access.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Secure- Park Mark security status.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Grove Road, Slip End, Luton, LU1 4BZ</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the M1:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;Leave the motorway at junction 10.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;Take the exit for Luton and the airport.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From the A1:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;Follow the A505 into Luton.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;At the Airport Roundabout, follow signs for “Other routes”, Parkway and the A505.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;At the next roundabout go straight on, following signs for the M1, St Albans and the A1081.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Then (from either direction):&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;Take the third exit at the next roundabout onto the A1081.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;Turn right onto Newlands Road, following signs for Airparks.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;Turn left onto the B4540, signposted Slip End and Markyate.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;At the traffic lights, turn right onto Grove Road.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;Take the first left onto the service road.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;Airparks will be on the right.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Pull up at the entrance barrier, which will lift after a few seconds (all cars coming into the site are recorded on CCTV). Park in one of the arrivals bays, then head into the check-in building. You check yourself in using the machines - it's a very quick process, though you'll need to have a copy of your booking confirmation with you. There's a member of staff on hand to help if you need it.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The machine will give you a tag, which you should attach to your keys, and a ticket, which you should keep safe as you'll need it later. Drop your keys in the box with the same number as the lane you've parked in. Your car will be parked for you, so just head to the waiting area and hop on the bus to the airport. You'll need to show your ticket to the driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If you have sports equipment or lots of luggage, you may need to wait for a bus with more space during busy times, so make sure you leave yourself plenty of time to get to the airport.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; The shuttle bus back to the car park leaves from bus stop 12 outside the terminal. You'll need to show the ticket you were given at check-in to the driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Make your way to the check-out shelter and follow the instructions on the key dispenser - again, it's a very quick process. The machine will give you your car key back and show you on the screen where your car is. Then just drive to the exit barrier - you'll need to scan the barcode attached to your keys, and then the barrier will lift.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Airparks Services is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>01582 749495  &lt;br /&gt; FAX: 01582 458936</helpline><distanceToAirport>Airparks is conveniently located about 4 miles from the airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers to the Terminal Building take about 12 minutes and are available 24 hours a day.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>12 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Airparks Services has a secure perimeter, patrols, CCTV and floodlighting. The car park also holds the 'Park Mark' safer parking award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>Mobile homes, lorries, caravans,trailers and high sided vehicles are not permitted.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>All buses have disabled access.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LTNU.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LTNA</code><airport>LTN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>AIRPARKS DROP AND GO</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Money-Saving off-airport secure parking.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Transfers every 20 mins.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;15 minutes to terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Money- saving.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Quick &amp;amp; Easy.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Grove Road, Slip End, Luton, Beds LU1 4BZ&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Leave the M1 at junction 10.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; - At the roundabout, take the first exit from the north or the second exit from the south onto Airport Way A1081.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; - Keep in the left hand lane and take the slip road signposted St. Albans, Harpenden A1081.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; - You'll come out onto a roundabout where you should take the second exit onto St. Albans, Harpenden A1081.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; - Shortly after, turn right onto Newlands Road, following signs for Airparks. &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; - Turn left onto the B4540, signposted Slip End and Markyate.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; - At the traffic lights, turn right onto Grove Road.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; - Take the first left onto the service road &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; - You will see Airparks on the right.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Pull up at the entrance barrier, which will lift after a few seconds (all cars coming into the site are recorded on CCTV). Park in one of the arrivals bays, then head into the check-in building. You check yourself in using the machines - it's a very quick process, though you'll need to have a copy of your booking confirmation with you. There's a member of staff on hand to help if you need it.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The machine will give you a tag, which you should attach to your keys, and a ticket, which you should keep safe as you'll need it later. Drop your keys in the box with the same number as the lane you've parked in. Your car will be parked for you, so just head to the waiting area and hop on the bus to the airport. You'll need to show your ticket to the driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; If you have sports equipment or lots of luggage, you may need to wait for a bus with more space during busy times, so make sure you leave yourself plenty of time to get to the airport.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; The shuttle bus back to the car park leaves from bus stop 12 outside the terminal. You'll need to show the ticket you were given at check-in to the driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Make your way to the check-out shelter and follow the instructions on the key dispenser - again, it's a very quick process. The machine will give you your car key back and show you on the screen where your car is. Then just drive to the exit barrier - you'll need to scan the barcode attached to your keys, and then the barrier will lift.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Airparks Services is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>01582 749495 Vat No. 726 0035 69</helpline><distanceToAirport>Airparks is conveniently located about 4 miles from the airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Airparks operate transfers to and from the airport every 20 minutes which take 15 minutes.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>15 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Airparks Services has a secure perimeter, patrols, CCTV and floodlighting. The car park also holds the 'Park Mark' safer parking award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>Mobile homes, lorries, caravans,trailers and high sided vehicles are not permitted.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>All buses have disabled access.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LTNA.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LTNO</code><airport>LTN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>CARPARKZ MEET AND GREET SAVER</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Time-saving chauffeur service - No transfers to worry about.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Extra savings for non-flexible bookings.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Extra saving - Non flexible bookings. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Monitored 24 hours a day, has perimeter fencing and is patrolled regularly by security guards.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Your car is stores less than 2 miles away from the Airport. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Eaton Green Road, Luton, LU2 9HD</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;PLEASE CALL: 01582 728585 or 07968 550863 WHEN YOU ARE 30 MINUTES AWAY FROM THE AIRPORT.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M1:&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit the M1 motorway at Junction 10 and proceed to the 1st roundabout.(You should contact our office by the time you reach this point)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout take the 2nd exit (straight on) on to the dual carriageway. (A1081 heading to Luton/Hitchin/A505).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the bottom of the hill, go through the traffic lights and stay in the left hand lane. (Follow the signs to the airport).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout (Holiday Inn Express), take the 3rd exit (straight on) towards the terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Go round the main terminal roundabout and follow the signs for the Short Term car park. (sign posted Offsite Meet &amp;amp; Greet parking).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Once past the entrance barrier you will see the Meet &amp;amp; Greet area on your right.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Please note that the Airport charges &amp;pound;3.80 to exit this area but the collecting driver would normally ask you to contribute just &amp;pound;1 towards this.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From Hitchin:&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From Hitchin Road/A505 head southwest.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Stopsley Way/A505. (Go past the Fire Station on the left.)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout take the 1st exit onto Vauxhall Way/A505.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Go through 1 roundabout.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Go through another roundabout (straight on)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the next roundabout (Vauxhall showroom) take the 1st exit (left) onto Airport Way.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout (Holiday Inn Express), take the 3rd exit (straight on) towards the terminal.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Go round the main terminal roundabout and follow the signs for the Short Term car park. (sign posted Offsite Meet &amp;amp; Greet parking).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Once past the entrance barrier you will see the Meet &amp;amp; Greet area on your right.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Please note that the Airport charges &amp;pound;3.80 to exit this area but the collecting driver would normally ask you to contribute just &amp;pound;1 towards this.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>PLEASE CALL: 07551 030862 WHEN YOU ARE 30 MINUTES AWAY FROM THE AIRPORT. On arrival at the airport you will be met in the Short Term Car Park. The Meet &amp;amp; Greet area is on the right hand side next to the pay-point station.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>On your return to Luton Airport, please call your chauffeur once you have cleared the terminal building. Your vehicle will be returned to you at the Meet &amp;amp; Greet area in the Short Term Car Park. Please note there is a fee, set by the airport, of &amp;pound;1 to exit the car park and that you will need to leave the car park within 10 minutes to avoid additional charges. Full return instructions will be provided to you by the chauffeur when your vehicle is collected.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Carparkz Park &amp;amp; Ride is open every day except Christmas Day.</openingPeriods><helpline>07551 030862</helpline><distanceToAirport>Your vehicle will be stored at Carparkz Meet &amp;amp; Greet's secure car park which is located less than 2 miles from the Terminal building.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required as this is a meet and greet service. Your car is collected and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Carparkz Park &amp;amp; Ride is monitored 24 hours a day, has perimeter fencing and is patrolled regularly by security guards.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LTNO.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LTNP</code><airport>LTN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>CARPARKZ PARK AND RIDE SAVER</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Convenient &amp;amp; economic off-airport parking.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Extra savings for non-flexible bookings.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Extra saving - Non flexible booking.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Carparkz Park &amp;amp; Ride is monitored 24 hours a day&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Perimeter fencing and is patrolled regularly by security guards.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Eaton Green Road, Luton, LU2 9HD</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Please allow at least 30 minutes for your transfer to Luton Airport.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M1:&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit the M1 motorway at Junction 10 and proceed to the 1st roundabout.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout take the 2nd exit (straight on) on to the dual carriageway. (A1081 heading to Luton/Hitchin/A505).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the bottom of the hill, go through the traffic lights and stay in the right hand lane. (sign posted Hitchin A505). Do not follow the signs to the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout (Vauxhall factory) take the 2nd exit (straight on) onto Vauxhall Way (sign posted Hitchin A505).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the next roundabout take the 3rd exit (turning right) onto Eaton Green Road (sign posted Tea Green).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;After 80m take the 1st right before the Shell garage and opposite The Wyvern bar &amp;amp; Grill.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Drive into the reception area and check in at the site.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From Hitchin:&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From Hitchin Road/A505 head southwest.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Stopsley Way/A505. (Go past the Fire Station on the left.)&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the roundabout take the 1st exit onto Vauxhall Way/A505.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Go through 1 roundabout.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the next roundabout take the 1st exit onto Eaton Green Road.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;After 80m take the 1st right before the Shell garage and opposite The Wyvern bar &amp;amp; Grill.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Drive into the reception area and check in at the site.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Please allow at least 30 minutes for your transfer to Luton Airport. On arrival, please go to reception to check-in. Once you have checked in take the free shuttle bus to the airport.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>On your return please call 07551 030862 or 07968 550863. The shuttle bus will collect you from the Drop-Off Zone outside the terminal building.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Carparkz Park &amp;amp; Ride is open every day except Christmas Day.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt;01582 728585&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;07968 550863&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>Carparkz Park &amp;amp; Ride is located less than 2 miles from the Terminal building.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers to the Airport Terminal run regularly, take between 5 to 15 minutes depending on local traffic and are available 24 hours a day.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>5 - 15 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Carparkz Park &amp;amp; Ride is monitored 24 hours a day, has perimeter fencing and is patrolled regularly by security guards.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>4</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LTNP.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LTNR</code><airport>LTN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>CENTRAL CAR STORAGE MEET &amp; GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Quality chauffeur parking service - Ideal when time is tight!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Buy With Confidence Award.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Convenient and time-saving&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;You car will be located in a secure car park&amp;nbsp; 1 mile away.&amp;nbsp; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Secure - Park Mark security status. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Buy with confidence award. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Kimpton Road, Luton, Bedfordshire, LU2 0SX</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; PLEASE CALL 01582 726960 or 07864 707233 WHEN YOU ARE 10 MINUTES FROM ARRIVING AT THE AIRPORT. If coming by the M1 motorway, please telephone us as you leave the motorway or if coming another route, please telephone just before approaching the airport this gives our drivers time to meet you at the same time.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Coming from M1 Junction 10&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Sat Nav Postcode is LU2 9LY&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; After leaving Junction 10, follow signs to A1081, Luton and Airport, keep in the middle lane for Hitchin, Capability Green and Bus Park. Keep going straight, at the traffic lights, keep in left hand lane, follow signs to airport, at the Large roundabout at the top, take the third exit, passing the Holiday Express Hotel, you will go under the tunnel which welcomes you to Luton, it then goes into two lanes, keep right, and follow signs to Short Term car park, not Drop Off Point, please take a ticket at the barrier, and the Meet and Greet area, is on the right hand side, next to the Pay Station, please hand your paperwork and barrier ticket to our driver.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Coming from Hitchin A505&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Sat Nav Postcode is LU2 9LY&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From Hitchin A505, follow signs to Luton, you will pass a Hilton Hotel, on your right, be careful speed camera ahead, at large roundabout, take second exit, passing fire station, at next roundabout, take first exit, &amp;nbsp;signposted other routes, A505 and Motorway,&amp;nbsp; at next roundabout, second exit, signposted A505 and Town Centre, at the next roundabout, take the third exit, signposted, Town Centre, and Parkway. Next roundabout, take first &amp;nbsp;exit, at roundabout at top of the hill take the second exit, passing the Holiday Express Hotel, you will go under the tunnel which welcomes you to Luton, it then goes into two lanes, keep right, and follow signs to Short Term car park, not Drop Off Point, please take a ticket at the barrier, and the Meet and Greet area, is on the right hand side, next to the Pay Station, please hand your paperwork and barrier ticket to our driver&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>PLEASE CALL 01582 726960 or 07864 707233 WHEN YOU ARE 10 MINUTES FROM ARRIVING AT THE AIRPORT. If coming by the M1 motorway, please telephone us as you leave the motorway or if coming another route, please telephone just before approaching the airport this gives our drivers time to meet you at the same time. Make your way to the Short Term Car Park. Take a ticket and enter the car park. The Meet &amp;amp; Greet area is on the right hand side and is sign posted. Please give the entry ticket and parking voucher to our driver and please confirm your dates, return flight and arrival times.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On your return, please collect your luggage, clear customs and exit the terminal before telephoning us, we will then bring your car back to the Short Stay Car Park. Please note there is a fee, set by the airport, of &amp;pound;4.00 to exit the car park and that you will need to leave the car park within 10 minutes to avoid additional charges. Full return instructions will be provided on arrival at the car park.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Central Car Storage is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt;01582 726189&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;FREEPHONE: 0800 298 5899&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;MOBILE: 07864 707233&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;FAX: 01582 720957&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>Central Car Storage Off Airport Parking is located 1 mile from the airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required as this is a meet and greet service. Your car is collected and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Central Car Storage has CCTV, 15ft high security fencing and is manned 24 hours a day. The car park also holds the 'Park Mark' safer parking award.Buy with Confidence Award&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>48</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LTNR.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LTNQ</code><airport>LTN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>CENTRAL CAR STORAGE OFF AIRPORT PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Quality parking service located just 1mile from Luton Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Buy With Confidence Award.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Located 1 mile from the Luton Airport. &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Quality parking with peace of mind at Luton Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Open 24 hours a day. &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Central Car Storage has CCTV&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;15ft high security fencing and is manned 24 hours a day.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Kimpton Road, Luton, Bedfordshire, LU2 0SX</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Coming from M1 Junction 10&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; After leaving Junction 10, follow signs to A1081, Luton and Airport, keep in the middle lane for Hitchin, Capability Green and Bus Park. Keep going straight, at the traffic lights, turn left towards Town Centre and Dunstable, keep in left hand, turn left at the roundabout, passing the Retail park on your right, Venue 360 on left, at lights go straight, at the mini roundabout, second exit, to the next mini roundabout, turn right, which is second exit, sign posted IBC, and Chamber of Commerce, this is Kimpton Road, we are 150 yards on the right, opposite Hayward Tyler, into the service road into the Retail Park, we are on left, through the gates.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Coming from Hitchin A505&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; From Hitchin A505, follow signs to Luton, you will pass a Hilton Hotel, on your right, be careful speed camera ahead, at large roundabout, take second exit, passing fire station, at next roundabout, take first exit,&amp;nbsp; sign posted other routes, A505 and Motorway,&amp;nbsp; at next roundabout, second exit, signposted A505 and Town Centre, at the next roundabout, take the third exit, signposted Town Centre, and Parkway Station. Next roundabout, take third exit, this is Kimpton Road, passing Vauxhall showroom, on left, at roundabout straight over, passing Daily Express building, you will then pass the Hampton Hotel on the left, then a row of shops, you will go over the railway bridge, our entrance is 50 yards on left, the Retail park’s service road, For Sat Nav please use Postcode LU2 0SX, if asks for a number us No 22, which is next door to us.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Please report to the car park reception upon arrival. Please allow an extra 30 minutes for transfers at peak times.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Full return instructions will be provided on arrival at the car park.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Central Car Storage is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt;01582 726189 or 01582 726960&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;FAX: 01582 720957&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>Central Car Storage Off Airport Parking is located 1 mile from the airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers to and from the Terminal Building run on demand and take 5 minutes.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>5 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Central Car Storage has CCTV, 15ft high security fencing and is manned 24 hours a day. The car park also holds the 'Park Mark' safer parking award.Buy with Confidence Award&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>4</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LTNQ.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LTNT</code><airport>LTN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>DRIVEFLY LUTON MEET &amp; GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Chauffeur parking service - No time-consuming transfers necessary.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Chauffeur Service.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Drop-off/ Pick up in Short Stay Car Park&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Secure car park compound &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Manned - 24 hours a day. &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Fully insured&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;CCTV&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;br /&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;Drivefly will call 20 - 30 minutes prior to your booked arrival time to confirm the meet time. IT IS IMPORTANT THAT YOU CALL DRIVEFLY ON 07955 055777 or 07955 055700 IF YOU ARE RUNNING LATE OR EARLY.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M1: Exit at Junction 10/Junction 10A and follow the signs to Luton Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;On arrival at the airport, follow the signs to the Short Stay Car Park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take a ticket and enter the car park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Continue driving forward and park in the designated Meet &amp;amp; Greet pick up/drop off point which is next to the pay machine.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From Hitchin: Follow the A505 to Luton Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;On arrival at the airport, follow the signs to the Short Stay Car Park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take a ticket and enter the car park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Continue driving forward and park in the designated Meet &amp;amp; Greet pick up/drop off point which is next to the pay machine.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Drivefly will call 20 - 30 minutes prior to your booked arrival time to confirm the meet time. IT IS IMPORTANT THAT YOU CALL DRIVEFLY ON 07955 055777 or 07955 055700 IF YOU ARE RUNNING LATE OR EARLY. On arrival at the airport follow the signs for Short Stay parking. Take a ticket and enter the Short Stay car park. Continue driving forward and park in the designated Meet &amp;amp; Greet pick up/drop off point which is next to the pay machine. You will be met here by your chauffeur who will have your booking details and will be wearing a black jacket with the Drivefly company logo on it.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>On your return, please call 07955 055777 or 07955 055700 once you have collected all of your luggage. The chauffeur will deliver your vehicle to you at the pick-up point.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Drivefly Luton Meet &amp;amp; Greet is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>07955 055777 or 07955 055700</helpline><distanceToAirport>Drivefly Luton Meet &amp;amp; Greet is located 2 miles from the airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required as this is a meet and greet service. Your car is collected and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park is equipped with secure fencing and has 24 hour security patrols. The car park also holds the 'Park Mark' safer parking award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>24</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/LTNT.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>LTNS</code><airport>LTN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>LUTON BUDGET MEET AND  GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Economic and convenient chauffeur parking service.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Quick and efficient service. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Meet and Greet &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Your car is stored at our secure car park located 4 miles away. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Luton, Bedfordshire, LU1 4BZ</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;PLEASE CALL 07584 095985 WHEN YOU ARE 30 MINUTES AWAY FROM ARRIVING AT THE AIRPORT.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;London Luton Airport is only 30 minutes from North London, 15 minutes from the M25 and 5 minutes from the M1.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M1: The airport is just two miles from the M1 motorway.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit the M1 at Junction 10.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The route to the airport is clearly signposted. &lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the West: Access to London Luton Airport from the West is possible through several routes.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;If approaching via Dunstable, follow the airport signs.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the East: Access to London Luton Airport from the East and A1 is via the A505 dual carriageway through Hitchin.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The airport lies just off the A505 and is clearly signposted.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Alternative approaches include travelling via M40/M25 to join the M1 at Junction 21 and then exit via Junction 10.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>PLEASE CALL 07584 095985 WHEN YOU ARE 30 MINUTES AWAY FROM ARRIVING AT THE AIRPORT. On arrival at the airport follow the signs for the Short Stay Car Park and the chauffeur will meet you at the meeting point which is just through the barrier on the right.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt;Please call the chauffeur hotline on 07584 095 985 whilst you are waiting for your luggage. From receiving your call our chauffeur will be dispatched and will meet you in the meet &amp;amp; greet area within the short stay car park (where you dropped your car off) and will normally be with you within 8 – 12 minutes from receiving your call.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;There is a fee set by the airport of &amp;pound;1 for the first 15 minutes which you will be required to pay, and if you go over the 15 minutes the fee goes up to &amp;pound;4.50&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Luton Budget Meet &amp;amp; Greet is open 365 days a year. Arrivals are not accepted between 23.00 and 04.00.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>07584 095985 (Chauffeur Number)</helpline><distanceToAirport>Your car will be parked at a secure car park located about 4 miles from the airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Luton Budget Meet &amp;amp; Greet has a secure storage facility with perimeter fencing; barriers; CCTV and 24 hour security patrols.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>48</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>This service is ideal for disabl