scription><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Cars are kept at the APH secure car park which located 4 miles from the Airport. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Park Mark&amp;reg; Safer Parking Award&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Manned 24 hours &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;CCTV&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Entry and exit barriers&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Bradnor Road, Sharston Industrial Area, Manchester, M22 4TE</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Please contact APH on 0161 945 8122 fifteen minutes prior to your arrival at the terminal.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Manchester International Airport has its own dedicated exit on the M56 (J5).&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Exit the M56 at Junction 5.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the cube colour signs to your terminal of departure.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &lt;br /&gt; FOR TERMINAL 1:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow signs for Terminal 1 Departures, go into drop off area at the far end.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; An APH chauffeur wearing an orange jacket and an APH identity badge will meet you at the designated collection point for your terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &lt;br /&gt; FOR TERMINAL 2:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow signs for Terminal 2 Departures, go to the far end of the Departure level.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; An APH chauffeur wearing an orange jacket and an APH identity badge will meet you at the designated collection point for your terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &lt;br /&gt; FOR TERMINAL 3:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt; Follow signs T3 Departures, the driver will meet you in the ‘Drop off Area’&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt; An APH chauffeur wearing an orange jacket and an APH identity badge will meet you at the designated collection point for your terminal.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &lt;br /&gt; PLEASE NOTE TERMINALS 1 &amp;amp; 3 HAVE A HEIGHT RESTRICTION OF 2.0 M (6 FT 6INS). If your vehicle exceeds this please call the car park in advance and we will give you an alternative pick up point.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Please contact APH on 0161 945 8122 fifteen minutes prior to your arrival at the terminal. An APH chauffeur wearing an orange jacket and an APH Identity Badge will meet you at the designated collection point for your terminal. On arrival the chauffeur will check your booking details, mileage and for any vehicle damage, before issuing you with a receipt for your car.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Full instructions for the returns procedure will be issued to you by the chauffeur on arrival at the terminal.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>The car park is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0161 945 8122  &lt;br /&gt;Fax: 0161 946 1186</helpline><distanceToAirport>APH is located approximately 4 miles from the airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park has barrier control, CCTV and holds the 'Park Mark' safer parking award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>There is a vehicle height restriction of 2.0m or 6.5ft for Terminals 1 &amp;amp; 3. If your vehicle exceeds this please call the car park in advance and we will give you an alternative pick up point.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>This service is ideal for disabled travellers.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/MANZ.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>MAND</code><airport>MAN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>APH PARK AND RIDE</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Excellent service from specialists with 30 years of Airport Parking experience.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt; Winners for the fourth year running of the Best Airport Parking category at the British Travel Awards.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;CUSTOMERS FAVOURITE&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Park Mark Safer Parking Award&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;CCTV&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Barrier controlled entrance and exit system&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;24-hour security patrols&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Choose from indoor or outdoor parking&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Regular transfers, 24 hours a day&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Bradnor Road, Sharston Industrial Area,,Manchester, M22 4TE.</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M60 Anti-Clockwise: Exit at Junction 5 and take the A5103 towards Manchester Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the 2nd junction turn left onto the A560.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Carry on over the next roundabout and at the 2nd roundabout turn left onto the B5168, Sharston Road.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the 1st left onto Bradnor Road and APH is located on the right.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M60 Clockwise: Exit at Junction 4 onto the M56.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit the M56 at Junction 2 and take the 3rd exit onto the B5168, Sharston Road.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the 1st left onto Bradnor Road and APH is located on the right.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From Cheshire: Join the M56.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Exit at Junction 3a and turn right onto the A560.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Carry on over the next roundabout and at the 2nd roundabout turn left onto the B5168, Sharston Road.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the 1st left onto Bradnor Road and APH is located on the right.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>On arrival at car park report to reception and present your confirmation slip or quote your Booking Reference number.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Full instructions for the return procedure will be issued on arrival at the car park.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>The car park is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>0161 945 8122 Car Park telephone number Vat No. 726 0035 69</helpline><distanceToAirport>APH is located approximately 4 miles from the airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>APH operate transfers to and from the airport every 10 - 15 minutes which take 5 minutes.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>5 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park has barrier control, CCTV and holds the 'Park Mark' safer parking award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>There is a vehicle height restriction of 2.0m or 6.5ft for Terminals 1 &amp;amp; 3. If your vehicle exceeds this please call the car park in advance and we will give you an alternative pick up point.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>This service is ideal for disabled travellers.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/MAND.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>MANS</code><airport>MAN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>DMD MANCHESTER PARK AND RIDE</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Cost-effective off-airport parking.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Security barriers&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;CCTV&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Guard dogs &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Has been granted the Park Mark Safer Parking award. &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Undercover parking is available. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Boundary Farm, Styal Road, Manchester, M22 5YA</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;DMD Park &amp;amp; Ride is located about 2 miles from Manchester Airport which is located at Junction 5 of the M56 motorway.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M56: Exit at Junction 5 (Manchester Airport).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for Terminal 1.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the end of the slip road stay in the left hand lane.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for Cheadle.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Continue through the road works still following the signs for Cheadle.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Once clear of all the road works the runway will be on your right hand side.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Continue along Ringway Road to the end.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the traffic lights turn right onto Styal Road (Shell Petrol station on right hand corner).&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Continue for approximately 500 metres passing Jet Parks 3 on the right.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The entrance to DMD Park &amp;amp; Ride is located immediately after the row of four cottages. Look for the car park signs at the hedgerow.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>On arrival at the car park you will be greeted by a member of staff who will help you to unload and will then park your car. You will be required to leave your keys. You will then be escorted to one of DMD's luxury mini-coaches and driven to your departure terminal. Please note that there is an extra charge of &amp;pound;7.50 per week for vans and &amp;pound;10 per week for commercial vehicles or motorhomes, which is payable directly to the car park on arrival.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>Please call 0161 498 9119 after you have collected your luggage and have cleared Customs. You will then be given instructions on where we will collect you from.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>DMD Manchester Park &amp;amp; Ride is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt;0161 498 9119&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Fax: 0161 498 6221&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>DMD Manchester Park &amp;amp; Ride is located 2 miles from the airport.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers to and from the airport operate 24 hours a day and take just 3 minutes. Transfers operate every 20 minutes in the summer and on the hour and half past the hour during the winter.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>3 minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>DMD Manchester Park &amp;amp; Ride has security barriers, CCTV, guard dogs and has been granted the Park Mark safer parking award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>Please note there is an additional charge for vans, payable directly to the car park on arrival.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>Perfect for the disabled traveller as our chauffeur will carry out the transfer procedure and help with your luggage.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/MANS.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>MANP</code><airport>MAN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>EAZYPARK MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Convenient chauffeur service - No time-consuming transfers.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Service is available for all three terminals. &lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The car park is secure with Palisade fencing with razor wire on top&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Manned 24 hours&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;The car park also holds the 'PARK MARK' safer parking award.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Boundary Farm, Styal Road, Manchester, M22 5YA</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;PLEASE CALL 07921 145602 - 20 MINUTES BEFORE ARRIVING AT THE AIRPORT TO ARRANGE THE MEETING DESIGNATION WITH THE CHAUFFEUR.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the M56: Exit at Junction 5 which is a dedicated exit for Manchester International Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs for Departures at the Terminal that you require. An Eazypark driver will meet you there. &lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>IMPORTANT - PLEASE CALL 07921 145602 - 20 MINUTES BEFORE ARRIVING AT THE AIRPORT TO ARRANGE THE MEETING DESIGNATION WITH THE CHAUFFEUR.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; On your return call once you have collected your luggage and cleared customs. A chauffeur will then return your vehicle to the terminal.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; IMPORTANT - Due to roadworks in the area there may be a delay with the return of your vehicle.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Eazypark Ltd Meet &amp;amp; Greet is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 07921 145602, Emergency No: 07854 015240&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Vat No. 726 0035 69&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>Your car will be parked at our secure car park which is located 5 miles from the Terminal Buildings.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>The car park is protected with Palisade fencing with razor wire on top and is manned 24hrs a day. The car park also holds the 'PARK MARK' safer parking award.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&amp;nbsp;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>48</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>Perfect for the disabled traveller as our chauffeur will carry out the transfer procedure and help with your luggage.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/MANP.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>MANG</code><airport>MAN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>JETPARKS RINGWAY</name><description>&lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Brand new car park - Introductory price.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Free buses to all three Terminals.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Keep hold of your keys.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Free bus transfer to and from all three terminals&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Keep hold of your keys&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Secure - Park Mark security status&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Official airport car park&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Operates Automatic Number Plate Recognition (ANPR), for simple entry and exit&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Well lit parking for arrivals during hours of darkness&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; JetParks Ringway, Shadowmoss Road, Manchester&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Exit the M56 at Junction 5. Keep left and take the 1st exit signposted Terminal 2.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; At the end of the slip road, join the roundabout and take the 1st exit. Carry on until you reach the traffic lights.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; At the traffic lights follow signs for Cheadle B5166. Pass the next two sets of traffic lights and then take the next left on to Shadowmoss Road.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; The entrance to JetParks Ringway will be 100 yards on your right.&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Drive up to the barrier which will recognise your number plate and open automatically. Drive in and park in any space. If there are any problems press the intercom button for help.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; After collecting your luggage, get the bus back to the car park. Drive up to the exit barrier, which will open. If there are any problems press the intercom button for help.&amp;nbsp;If prompted to settle an over-stay payment please use the integrated chip and pin device.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>The car park is open 365 days a year.</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0871 310 2200&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; 7-13 minutes away from the Airport.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Free 24 hour bus transfer to and from all three terminals every 15 minutes, taking 7-13 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>7 - 13 Minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Secure car park with barriers, CCTV and 24-hour patrols.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/MANG.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>MAN1</code><airport>MAN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>MANCHESTER AIRPORT MULTI-STOREY 1</name><description>&lt;li&gt;Located next to Terminal 1.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Perfect if you have heavy or bulky luggage.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;br /&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Perfect for time precious business travellers and leisure travellers.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Under-cover parking and same level terminal access available&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Keep hold of your keys&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Secure -Park Mark&amp;nbsp;status&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Official airport car park&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Operates Automatic Number Plate Recognition&amp;nbsp;(ANPR), for simple entry and exit.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Well lit parking for arrivals during hours of darkness&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Manchester Airport, M90 1QX</address><directions>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Leave the M56 at Junction 5.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Keep in the right hand lane and follow the signposts for Terminal's 1 and 3.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;You will see the Hilton Hotel, followed quickly by Bewleys Hotel, on your left hand side.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the ramp to the left and enter the car park