ion><furtherInformation>Convenient chauffeur meet &amp;amp; greet service.,Includes a Car wash &amp;amp; Dry</furtherInformation><address>Norwich International Airport, Amsterdam Way, Norwich, NR6 6JA</address><directions>&lt;p&gt;IMPORTANT: Please call 07876 717674 when you are approximately 20 minutes from the airport to confirm your arrival time.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the West: Take the A11 to Norwich.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Turn left onto the A140 and follow the directions below.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the East: Take the A47 to Norwich.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At Postwick take the A1042 Norwich Ring Road.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Carry on along the A1042 until it meets the A140.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Take the A140 North to Norwich Airport and follow the directions below.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;From the North/South: Take the A140 to Norwich Airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the airport crossroads, turn into Amsterdam Way towards the airport.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;At the 1st roundabout head straight over keeping on Amsterdam Way.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Follow the signs to the Short Stay car park.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>Please call 07876 717674 when you are approximately 20 minutes from the airport to confirm your arrival time. On arrival at Norwich Airport, drive to the drop off point in the short stay car park. Please take the ticket issued at the barrier and pass it to your driver. A Drop &amp;amp; Go representative, identified by a board displaying the Drop &amp;amp; Go Logo will be waiting in the drop and pick up area. While you unload your luggage we will check in your car.</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>When you have collected your baggage please telephone 07876 717674 to receive details of where your driver will meet you with your vehicle.</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>Drop &amp;amp; Go Parking is open from 04:00 to 23:00 every day.</openingPeriods><helpline>01603 754428</helpline><distanceToAirport>Drop &amp;amp; Go Parking's car park is located about 1 mile from the airport terminal.</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required with this service as your car is collected from you and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>Drop &amp;amp; Go Parking has a secured storage site that is manned and fully fenced with on-site security patrols.</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>Drop &amp;amp; Go Parking are unable to accept lorries, vans, mobile homes or caravans.</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>48</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled>This service is ideal for disabled customers. On your return please call 07876 717674 and advise the chauffeur of that you require special assistance. Your car will then be delivered back to you at one of the disabled bays on the first aisle of the Short Stay car park.</facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/NWIB.jpg</logoURL></carPark></carParks></airport><airport code=\"PIK\"><name>Prestwick Airport</name><shortname>prestwickairport</shortname><terminals><terminal>1</terminal></terminals><carParks/></airport><airport code=\"SOU\"><name>Southampton International Airport</name><shortname>southamptoninternationalairport</shortname><terminals><terminal>1</terminal></terminals><carParks><carPark><code>SOUE</code><airport>SOU</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>CRUISE PARKING PARK AND RIDE</name><description>&lt;li&gt;PLEASE NOTE THIS CAR PARK IS ONLY FOR SOUTHAMPTON FERRY PORT&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Drop your car and go.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Convenient and great value.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Fully trained and insured drivers will park your car for you.&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Service only available those traveling on CRUISE OR FERRY.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Convenient and great value. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Park Mark Award for safer parking.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Security barrier for restricted access.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;CCTV coverage of the car park.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Full security fencing of the perimeter.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Security lighting over the facility.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Regular staff security patrols.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Cruise Parking Ltd, Unit H1 Cracknore Hard, Marchwood, Southampton, SO40 4ZD&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Leave the M27 at junction 3 and join the M271, following signs for Southampton docks.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; Follow the M271 for 1.5 miles. &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; At the first roundabout take the second exit, signposted A35 to Totton and Lyndhurst and A326 to Fawley.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; At the traffic lights, the road merges with the A35. Continue along the A35 for one mile, following signs for Lyndhurst. Do not follow signs to Totton town centre.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; At the next roundabout turn left, following signs for the A326 and Marchwood.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; Continue for half a mile to the traffic lights. Turn left into Jacobs Gutter Lane, following signs for Marchwood.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; After 1.5 miles turn left at the roundabout into Normandy Way, following signs for Marchwood Industrial Park, Cracknore Hard and Hythe.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; After half a mile you will come to Marchwood Industrial Park. Go straight on at the mini roundabout, then turn left into Cracknore Hard. The car park is signposted from here.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; You will pass McMullen Barracks on your left and the Sea Mounting Centre on your right. Turn right into Harbour Close. Follow the road round to the left and drive through the second set of gates on the right.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; You should arrive at the car park at least two hours before you are due to sail.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; A member of staff will show you where to leave your car and go through the paperwork with you. You'll just leave your car in one of the arrivals lanes, which are right next to the bus stop - Cruise Parking will park your car for you, so you'll need to leave your keys with them.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Make your way to the heated waiting room with seats, toilets and a drinks machine to wait for the bus. It runs between 10:00 and 18:00, whenever it's needed, takes 15 minutes to get to the port and is included in the price for up to four passengers. If more than four people are travelling, you'll need to pay &amp;pound;10 to the car park.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; PLEASE NOTE THIS CAR PARK IS ONLY FOR SOUTHAMPTON FERRY PORT. IT IS NOT POSSIBLE TO REACH SOUTHAMPTON AIRPORT FROM THIS CAR PARK.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Catch the bus back to the car park. It runs between 06:00 and 12:00. It will pick you up from bay 25 at the Ocean cruise terminal, bay 26 at the City cruise terminal and bay 20 at the Mayflower cruise terminal. If you're coming into the Queen Elizabeth II terminal, you'll need to ask a member of Cruise Parking staff where to get the bus - there'll be someone either in the terminal or outside by the coach bays.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Cruise Parking is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 0845 270 7585&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;br /&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; Transfers run frequently to and from the port and take around 15 minutes. You will be dropped off / collected from the drop off point at the relevant cruise terminal that you are sailing from.&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>Transfers take approximately 15 minutes.</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Cruise Parking Ltd has Park Mark Award and is fully secure – Fenced and lit. It has CCTV and is manned throughout the day. Security patrols operate throughout the night.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>48</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/SOUE.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>SOUD</code><airport>SOU</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>STRESS FREE CRUISE PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;PLEASE NOTE THIS CAR PARK IS ONLY FOR SOUTHAMPTON FERRY PORT&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;You will be met at the Port.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Drop your car off at the Docking Station, no need for bus transfers&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Meet and Greet. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;We will store your vehicle in a secure car park nearby which has 24 hour manned security and security fencing with barbed wire.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;You will be met at the PORT.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;No need for transfers&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;br /&gt;</furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Southampton Cruise Port, SO14 3QN&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; PLEASE NOTE THIS CAR PARK IS ONLY FOR SOUTHAMPTON FERRY PORT. IT IS NOT POSSIBLE TO REACH SOUTHAMPTON AIRPORT FROM THIS CAR PARK.&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; PLEASE CALL OUR CHAUFFEURS ON 07540 794007&amp;nbsp; WHEN YOU ARE 30 MINUTES AWAY FROM ARRIVING AT THE CRUISE PORT. YOUR CHAUFFEUR WILL THEN ARRANGE TO MEET YOU AT THE DOCKING STATION.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the North:&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take the M3 to Southampton and join the M27 West at Junction 14.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Exit the M27 at Junction 3 and take the M271 (S) to Southampton &amp;amp; the Docks.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the end of the M271 take the 1st exit on to the A33 towards the City Centre and the Docks.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the signs to the Waterfront.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the East/West:&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take the the M27 to Junction 3.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Join the M271 (S) to Southampton &amp;amp; the Docks.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; At the end of the M271 take the 1st exit on to the A33 towards the City Centre and the Docks.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Follow the signs to the Waterfront.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Address for SAT NAV:&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; City Cruise Terminal (Birth 101) - SO15 1HJ&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Ocean Cruise Terminal (Birth 46) - SO14 3QN&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Mayflower Cruise Terminal (Birth 106) - SO15 1HJ&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Queen Elizabeth 2 Terminal (Birth 38/39) - SO14 3GG&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Main Port postcode - SO14 3QN&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; PLEASE NOTE THIS CAR PARK IS ONLY FOR SOUTHAMPTON FERRY PORT. IT IS NOT POSSIBLE TO REACH SOUTHAMPTON AIRPORT FROM THIS CAR PARK.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; PLEASE CALL OUR CHAUFFEURS ON 07540 794007&amp;nbsp; WHEN YOU ARE 30 MINUTES AWAY FROM ARRIVING AT THE CRUISE PORT. YOUR CHAUFFEUR WILL THEN ARRANGE TO MEET YOU AT THE DOCKING STATION.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; QEII terminal -&amp;nbsp;Enter the docks through Dock Gate 4.&amp;nbsp; Then follow signs for your cruise ship.&amp;nbsp; Once at the cruise terminal, traffic marshals will direct to the right up a ramp into a large baggage drop off hanger.&amp;nbsp; Once you have unloaded your bags drive back out of this hanger and across the road into the sign posted short stay car park. &amp;nbsp;The driver will be waiting for you here. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Ocean Terminal-&amp;nbsp;Enter the docks through Dock Gate 4.&amp;nbsp; Then follow signs for your cruise ship.&amp;nbsp; Once at the cruise terminal, traffic marshals will direct you into the baggage drop off lanes.&amp;nbsp; Once you have unloaded your bags, drive across into the short stay car park.&amp;nbsp; The short stay car park is adjacent to the drop off lanes less than 20 metres away.&amp;nbsp; Enter through either entrance barrier, and please be mind-full to keep hold of your parking ticket to give to our driver.&amp;nbsp; The driver will be waiting for you towards the end of the car park, close to the grey booth.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; City Terminal -&amp;nbsp;Enter the docks through either Dock Gate 8 or 10.&amp;nbsp; Then follow signs for your cruise ship.&amp;nbsp; Once at the cruise terminal, traffic marshals will direct into the baggage drop off lanes.&amp;nbsp; Once you have unloaded your bags please drive across into the sign posted short stay car park.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; The driver will be waiting for you here.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Mayflower -&amp;nbsp;Enter the docks through Dock Gate 10.&amp;nbsp; Then follow signs for your cruise ship.&amp;nbsp; Once at the cruise terminal, traffic marshals will direct into the under-cover baggage drop off lanes.&amp;nbsp; Once you have unloaded your bags please drive across into the sign posted short stay car park.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; The short stay car park is just about opposite the large ‘Departures’ end of the drop off lanes.&amp;nbsp; So when exiting these lanes turn back on yourself and the short stay is just over the zebra crossing on your left. The driver will be waiting for you here.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; PLEASE NOTE THIS CAR PARK IS ONLY FOR SOUTHAMPTON FERRY PORT. IT IS NOT POSSIBLE TO REACH SOUTHAMPTON AIRPORT FROM THIS CAR PARK.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; When you know what time you are disembarking, please call the chauffeur number to arrange the return of your car.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; PLEASE NOTE THIS CAR PARK IS ONLY FOR SOUTHAMPTON FERRY PORT. IT IS NOT POSSIBLE TO REACH SOUTHAMPTON AIRPORT FROM THIS CAR PARK.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Cruise Parking is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 07540 794007&amp;nbsp; (Chauffeur Hotline)&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required as this is a meet and greet service. Your car is collected and returned to you at the port.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Cruise Parking Ltd has Park Mark Award and is fully secure – Fenced and lit. It has CCTV and is manned throughout the day. Security patrols operate throughout the night.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>48</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/SOUD.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>SOUC</code><airport>SOU</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>STRESS FREE MEET AND GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;You will be met at the Terminal.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Drop your car off at the Airport, no need for bus transfers&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation>&lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;You will be met at the Terminal&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt;Drop your car off at the Airport&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;</furtherInformation><address>Southampton Airport, SO18 2NL</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; PLEASE CALL 02380 658223&amp;nbsp; WHEN YOU ARE 20 MINUTES AWAY FROM ARRIVING AT THE AIRPORT&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Southampton Airport can be found just off of the M27 Motorway at Junction 5.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M27: Exit at Junction 5 and take the A335, following the signs to the airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M3: Exit at Junction 14, joining the M27 East.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Exit the M27 at Junction 5.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take the 2nd exit on the roundabout, the A335, and follow the signs to the airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Arrival&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Call 02380 658223 and select option 2, 20 minutes before you arrive to make sure a driver is waiting for you.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Enter the Short Stay car park and follow signs for the Drop off/Pick up area. If you need to take a ticket then do so, but make sure to keep it and hand it to the driver. Park and a uniformed driver will find you. The driver will quickly inspect your car, to confirm any existing damage, then take your keys and park your car for you.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Please have your return flight details and booking confirmation to hand when you meet the driver.&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Return&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Call 02380 658223, option 2 when you are ready to collect your car. To leave as soon as possible, call just after you leave the plane. A driver will be waiting with your car where you were met before your holiday and will have a ticket to let you exit the car park. The driver can only wait for you for ten minutes, due to airport restrictions, so don't call until you are ready to leave.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; Cruise Parking is open 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 02380 658223&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport></distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>Transfers are not required as this is a meet and greet service. Your car is collected and returned to you at the airport.</transferFromAirport><transferTime>N/A</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; Cruise Parking Ltd has Park Mark Award and is fully secure – Fenced and lit. It has CCTV and is manned throughout the day. Security patrols operate throughout the night.&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize></maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>48</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/SOUC.jpg</logoURL></carPark></carParks></airport><airport code=\"SEN\"><name>Southend Airport</name><shortname>southendairport</shortname><terminals/><carParks><carPark><code>SENF</code><airport>SEN</airport><serviceType>P</serviceType><name>PURPLE PARKING</name><description>&lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Only 1.2 miles away from the Airport.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Transfers run on demand and take approximately 2 minutes&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation></furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Unit D Millhead Way, Purdeys Industrial Estate, Rochford, Essex SS4 1LB&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Getting to SACP Car Park couldn’t be easier if you follow these simple directions.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Join the M25 Motorway and head for Dartford Crossing.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Leave the M25 at junction 29 for the A127 towards Southend/Basildon.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Stay on the A127 for approx 18 miles&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; At the Tesco’s roundabout – go straight over (3rd exit) towards Southend (Princes Ave)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; At the next roundabout – turn left into Manners Way&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; At the next roundabout – turn right (4th exit) into Southend Road&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; At the next roundabout – turn right into Sutton Road&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; At the next roundabout – turn left into Purdeys Way&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the 2nd road on the right into Rochehall Way&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Take the 1st road on the left into Millhead Way&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Drive all the way to the end of the road and turn left where you will see the entrance to SACP Car Park.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; There will be signs at the entrance of the Car Park so please follow these signs and one of our car park attendants will be there to greet you on your arrival.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; For Sat Nav Directions please type in: SS4 1LB&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Our Full Address is:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; SACP &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Unit D Millhead Way&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Purdeys Industrial Estate&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Rochford&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; Essex&lt;/p&gt;</directions><arrivalProcedure>&lt;p&gt; When you arrive at SACP, a member of staff will process the necessary paperwork and then help you with your luggage onto the mini-bus. In no time at all you will be at the Terminal.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</arrivalProcedure><departureProcedure>&lt;p&gt; Once you have collected your luggage please make your way to the &amp;quot;Short Stay Car Park&amp;quot; once you are in the car park please call us on 07412 962929. Please do not phone us until you are in the Short Stay Car Park as each pick-up bus is only allowed 5 minutes to pick passengers up and then cannot re - enter the pick up zone for 15minutes meaning you will have to wait. Calling us before you are ready to leave the Terminal may result in you waiting longer for the pick-up bus to be allowed back in to pick you up.&lt;/p&gt;</departureProcedure><openingPeriods>&lt;p&gt; This car park is opened 365 days a year.&lt;/p&gt;</openingPeriods><helpline>&lt;p&gt; 07412 962929 (Customer: Collection/Drop Off)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; 03300 889540 (Reservations/Customer Service)&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</helpline><distanceToAirport>&lt;p&gt; SACP secure car park is located 1.2 miles from the airport.&lt;/p&gt;</distanceToAirport><transferFromAirport>&lt;p&gt; A mini-bus wil take you to and from the airport. Transfer to and from the airport will take 2 minutes and runs on demand. As soon as the customer turns up at the car park we will run straight down to the airport.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</transferFromAirport><transferTime>2 Minutes</transferTime><transferFrequency></transferFrequency><cancellations></cancellations><securityMeasures>&lt;p&gt; The car park is securely gated with CCTV, floodlights and is manned 24 hours a day.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; This car park hold the Park Mark Award.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</securityMeasures><maximumCarSize>&lt;p&gt; Purple Parking cannot accept bookings for caravans, trailers or buses.&lt;/p&gt;</maximumCarSize><leadTimeHours>0</leadTimeHours><facilitiesForDisabled></facilitiesForDisabled><mapURL></mapURL><errata></errata><logoURL>https://assets.purpleparking.com/products/badges/SENF.jpg</logoURL></carPark><carPark><code>SENG</code><airport>SEN</airport><serviceType>M</serviceType><name>PURPLE PARKING MEET &amp; GREET</name><description>&lt;li&gt;BRAND NEW!&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Meet our Chauffeur at the Terminal Building.&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;The ultimate parking service&lt;/li&gt;</description><furtherInformation></furtherInformation><address>&lt;p&gt; Unit D Millhead Way, Purdeys Industrial Estate, Rochford, Essex SS4 1LB&lt;/p&gt;</address><directions>&lt;p&gt; Please call 07412 962929 when you are 15 minutes away from the airport or have just passed the Basildon turn off to arrange your vehicle collection. If you are going to be early or late for your meet time please advise Purple Parking immediately.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt; From the M25: Exit at Junction 29.&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;li&gt; Take the A127 (Arterial Road) eastwards towards Southend.&lt;/li&gt;  